          "effect": "<strong>Core Passive — [blue]Any 3-Ping + Ping Red Orb[/blue]</strong>\nLucia: Lotus enters Burst Form when a Red Orb in pinged within 3s after any 3-Ping, replacing Basic Attacks with [red]Dual Blades[/red]. Lotus - Dual Blades: Attacks the enemy multiple times, dealing Physical DMG. \n- Deals [red]1080%[/red] Physical DMG in total.",
