          "memory": "Build:Eclipse",
          "bio": "A member of Gray Raven. As one of the newest support Constructs, she’s the anchor of the team.",
          "effect": "After any 3-Ping, the next Red Orb skill will unleash a laser cluster that deals Physical DMG. \n- Deals [red]800%[/red] Physical DMG in total.",
          "priority": "[red]Laser Shot[/red]'s Extra DMG Bonus increases by [red]50%[/red]. Gains [red]15%[/red] ATK after a 3-Ping for [red]5s[/red]. Duration resets every time it is triggered.",
          "notes": "- Any 3-Ping + [red]Red Orb Ping[/red] triggers <strong>Laser Cluster</strong> (Core Passive)\n- The [red]Red Orb Ping[/red] can be cast at any point after the 3-Ping (other orbs can be pinged in-between if needed, and there is no time limit within which you must cast the [red]Red Orb Ping[/red] after the 3-Ping)\n\n- Eclipse's [blue]Blue Orb Ping[/blue] will heal herself and any allies within the skill's circle\n\n- To heal off-field teammates when Eclipse is the on-field character, activate a teammate's QTE by performing a 3-Ping of that teammate's color, then trigger the QTE to temporarily bring that teammate on-field and cast Eclipse's [blue]Blue Orb Ping[/blue] while standing near them\n\n- To heal on-field teammates while Eclipse is off-field, have the on-field teammate activate a 3-Ping of Eclipse's assigned color, then trigger Eclipse's QTE to call her down and heal on-field allies within a fixed radius\n\n- <strong>Laser Cluster</strong> completely replaces the [red]Red Orb Ping[/red] used to activate it, so from an orb efficiency standpoint, it is usually preferable to use a [red]Red Orb 1-Ping[/red] or [red]2-Ping[/red] to trigger <strong>Laser Cluster</strong> when possible\n\n- <strong>Laser Cluster</strong> can be dodge-canceled upon activation with no damage penalty\n\n- Using a Yellow Orb 3-Ping to activate <strong>Laser Cluster</strong> works well when facing crowds, since Eclipse's Yellow Orb Ping will gather nearby enemies and allow all of them to take damage from <strong>Laser Cluster</strong>\n- Eclipse automatically performs a free Yellow Orb 3-Ping when switched in during combat, allowing for a quick activation of <strong>Laser Cluster</strong> with any additional [red]Red Orb Ping[/red]\n\n- When using a [blue]Blue Orb 3-Ping[/blue] to activate <strong>Laser Cluster</strong>, try to cast the [red]Red Orb Ping[/red] within 4 seconds of the [blue]Blue Orb 3-Ping[/blue] so that <strong>Laser Cluster</strong> will benefit from the [blue]Blue Orb Ping's[/blue] 5 second Physical DMG buff\n\nTrivia\n- On 25 August 2021, Ai Kayano's voice lines were removed from the CN version of PGR due to controversy\n- According to the Global branch team on 26 August 2021, Ai Kayano's voice will be removed on all servers\n\nCategory:Support\nCategory:Gray Raven\n__INDEX__",
