          "memory": "Build:Dawn",
          "bio": "Lucia’s signature frame. As graceful as it is powerful, its mere appearance on the battlefield inspires its allies, earning the “Dawn” sobriquet.",
          "effect": "<strong>Core Passive — [blue]Ping Yellow / Blue Orb + Tap Basic Attack (chance to trigger)[/blue]</strong>\n [red]Lightning Lure[/red]: Attacking a marked enemy has a chance to summon a lightning bolt to trike the target, dealing Lightning DMG. \n- There is a [red]25% / 50% / 75%[/red] chance to summon a lightning bolt that deals [red]60%[/red] Lightning DMG based on the number of marks on the enemy.",
          "priority": "Lightning DMG Bonus increases by [red]5%[/red] for [red]4s[/red] when dealing Lightning DMG. Can be stacked up to [red]4[/red] times. Signature Move increases own Extra DMG Bonus by [red]10%[/red] for [red]10s[/red]. Both duration will reset every time it is triggered.",
          "notes": "- Hitting enemies with a [blue]Blue Orb Ping[/blue] or Yellow Orb Ping tags them with a Lightning Mark\n- Up to 3 Lightning Marks can be stacked onto the same enemy, indicated by the number of lit lightning bolt icons above the enemy\n- Lightning Marks have a 12 second duration, after which all Lightning Marks on that enemy will expire\n- Lightning Mark's duration will be refreshed on another [blue]Blue Orb Ping[/blue] or Yellow Orb Ping hit\n\n- Casting Signature Move will activate Lotus Blade for 15 seconds\n- Any attacks launched by Dawn will trigger synchronized attacks from Lotus Blade that deal Lightning DMG\n\n- Landing a hit on an enemy with Lightning Marks has a chance to cause additional Lightning DMG on that hit\n- This chance is 25%/50%/75%, based on the number of Lightning Marks currently stacked onto that enemy\n\n- Mark enemies with Lightning Marks, then use high hit count attack sequences such as Dawn's [red]Red Orb Ping[/red] and any attacks launched with Lotus Blade active to trigger as many additional Lightning DMG instances as possible\n\n- Only the first hit of the [blue]Blue Orb Ping[/blue] and Yellow Orb Ping will apply a Lightning Mark; damage done by the fields deployed by Yellow Orb Pings cannot apply Lightning Marks\n\n- Recasting Lotus Blade before it expires will refresh its duration back to 15 seconds\n- This recast has a much shorter casting time and still grants invulnerability frames\n\n- Lotus Blade's duration continues counting down even when Dawn is off-field\n\n- Lotus Blade's duration will now pause while Dawn is off-field\n\n- Casting or recasting Lotus Blade will grant Dawn a 10% Extra DMG Bonus buff for 10 seconds, and regenerate a total of 20 Signature Energy over that period\n\n- The chance of triggering additional Lightning DMG when hitting an enemy with Lightning Marks increases to 50%/75%/100% based on the number of Lightning Marks on that enemy\n- The additional Lighting DMG dealt from these triggers is further increased\n\n- [red]Red Orb 3-Pings[/red] deal increased damage and weakly pull in nearby enemies\n- If Lotus Blade is active when a [red]Red Orb 3-Ping[/red] is cast, Basic Attack can be held down to trigger a follow-up attack that dashes Dawn through enemies in front of her",
