                  "description": "<strong>Yellow Orb — [blue]Ping Yellow Orb[/blue]</strong>\nCharges at the target dealing Physical DMG and Extra Dark DMG. When charging, reduces all damage taken from frontal attacks and becomes immune to control effects. \n- Deals [red]200% / 400% / 600%[/red] Physical DMG and [red]40% / 80% / 120%[/red] Extra Dark DMG based on the number of orbs pinged. \n- When charging, reduces all damage taken from frontal attacks by [red]30%[/red].\n\n<strong>Yellow Orb — [blue]Dark Form + Ping Yellow Orb[/blue]</strong>\nIn [red]Dark Form[/red], charges at the target to deal Dark DMG. When charging, reduces all damage taken from frontal attacks and becomes immune to control effects. \n- Deals [red]600% / 750% / 900%[/red] Dark DMG based on the number of orbs pinged.\n- When charging, reduces all damage taken from frontal attacks by [red]30%[/red].",
                  "icon": "YEL"
