                  "description": "Launches 2 quick attacks forward to deal Physical DMG. Upon a 3-Ping, Changyu: Qilin will charge up for a short while to launch a heavy blow after 2 quick attacks, dealing Ice DMG and slowing the enemies. \n- Deals [red]200% / 400% / 400%[/red] Physical DMG based on the number of orbs pinged. \n- The heavy blow deals [red]400%[/red] Ice DMG.",
