          "memory": "Build:Pavo",
          "bio": "A Transcendant and the last head of Kowloong. After the Battle of Kowloong, she has gone into hiding and continued with her ambition to achieve the Tabula Akasha.",
          "effect": "<strong>Core Passive — [blue]Ping any Orb[/blue]</strong>\nGains Sync Rate from pinging orbs. When the Sync Rate is at maximum, Signal Orbs are enhanced, and Qu: Pavo enters the [red]Concentrated Will State[/red] once an orb is pinged. \n- Every 1 orb pinged grants [red]10[/red] Sync Rate, up to [red]60[/red].\n\n<strong>Core Passive — [blue]Concentrated Will State[/blue]</strong>\nIn the [red]Concentrated Will State[/red], Signal Orbs can only be pinged individually. Pinging an orb consumes Sync Rate and triggers the corresponding 3-Ping skill and [red]Concentrated Will[/red], and will consume Sync Rate but generates no energy. In the [red]Concentrated Will State[/red], Sync Rate goes down over time. Once Sync Rate is empty, the [red]Concentrated Will State[/red] will end and Signal Orbs are no longer enhanced. \n- Each enhanced Signal Orb pinged consumes [red]20[/red] Sync Rate. In the [red]Concentrated Will State[/red], Sync Rate goes down by [red]5[/red] per second.\n\n<strong>Core Passive — [blue]Concentrated Will State + Ping Red Orb[/blue]</strong>\nRed Concentration: Bashes the ground to deal Physical DMG. \n- Deals [red]450%[/red] Physical DMG in total.\n\n<strong>Core Passive — [blue]Concentrated Will State + Ping Yellow Orb[/blue]</strong>\nYellow Concentration: Unleashes a shockwave forward to deal Physical DMG. \n- Deals [red]480%[/red] Physical DMG in total.\n\n<strong>Core Passive — [blue]Concentrated Will State + Ping Blue Orb[/blue]</strong>\nBlue Concentration: Releases a whirlwind that follows Qu: Pavo around, dealing Physical DMG to nearby enemies. \n- Deals [red]480%[/red] Physical DMG in total.",
          "priority": "Increases Physical DMG by [red]20%[/red] and Huiyu's attack frequency by [red]50%[/red]. Huiyu gains a new skill: [red]Curse Incarnate[/red]. [red]Curse Incarnate[/red]: Huiyu becomes a curse attached to the target, dealing up to [red]210%[/red] Physical DMG. It explodes after a short while to deal [red]240%[/red] Physical DMG. The DMG varies based on Qu's Signature Move level.",
