                  "description": "<strong>Signature Move — [blue]100 Energy + Tap Signature[/blue]</strong>\nCalls upon Huiyu to perform a combination attack that deals Physical DMG and grants Sync Rate. Qu: Pavo enters the [red]Concentrated Will State[/red], and Huiyu will attack enemies (prioritizing locked-on targets) continuously to deal Physical DMG. The Signature Move cannot be cast again when Huiyu exists. \n- Deals [red]1400%[/red] Physical DMG in total. \n- Casting the Signature grants [red]60[/red] Sync Rate. \n- Huiyu exists for [red]7[/red]s and deals [red]2240%[/red] Physical DMG in total.",
