          "memory": "Build:2B",
          "bio": "2B is an all-purpose battle android from the automated YoRHa infantry. She is equipped with a multitude of blades for close-quarters combat and can attack from range using the POD support system.",
          "effect": "<strong>Core Passive — [blue]Yellow 3-Ping + Any 3-Ping[/blue]</strong>\nAny 3-Ping after a Yellow 3-Ping grants 2B [red]Stability[/red]. [red]Stability[/red] decreases over time (re-triggering does not refresh the duration), While 2B has [red]Stability[/red], she enters [red]Battle Stance[/red]. Once 2B exits [red]Battle Stance[/red], all [red]Data Correction[/red] stacks will be removed. Obtaining additional stacks or unleashing Signature Move will refresh the duration of [red]Data Correction[/red]. While Signature Move is active, [red]Stability[/red] will not decrease. \n- Any 3-Ping after a Yellow 3-Ping grants 2B [red]160 Stability[/red]. \n- 2B loses [red]20 Stability[/red] per second.\n\n<strong>Core Passive — [blue]Battle Stance + Tap Basic Attack / Ping Yellow Orb[/blue]</strong>\nIn Battle Stance, Basic Attacks and Yellow Orbs also launch Swordwaves that deal Physical DMG. \n- Each Swordwave deals [red]70%[/red] Physical DMG.\n\n<strong>Core Passive — [blue]Battle Stance + Ping Red Orb[/blue]</strong>\nIn Battle Stance, Red Orbs also launch Swordwaves that deal Physical DMG and add [red]Data Correction[/red], granting Physical DMG Bonus. \n- Each Swordwave deals [red]70%[/red] Physical DMG. \n- [red]2 / 3[/red]-Ping Red Orbs will add [red]1 / 2[/red] stacks of [red]Data Correction[/red] that last [red]8[/red]s, stacking up to [red]3[/red] times. \n- Each stack of [red]Data Correction[/red] grants [red]2%[/red] Physical DMG Bonus (if 9S and A2 are also in the team, this effect increases to [red]4%[/red]).\n\n<strong>Core Passive — [blue]Battle Stance + Ping Blue Orb[/blue]</strong>\nIn [red]Battle Stance[/red], Blue Orbs can interrupt enemy attacks.",
          "priority": "Increases Physical DMG by [red]15%[/red] and doubles the effect of Leader Skill. Upon entering combat, gains [red]160 Stability[/red] and switching to [red]Battle Stance[/red] gives [red]2[/red] stacks of [red]Data Correction[/red].",
