          "bio": "A YoRHa prototype that specializes in close-quarter combat. Though not presently in use, it was originally created to speed along the implementation of other official models such as 2B and 9S.",
          "effect": "<strong>Core Passive — [blue]Any 3-Ping[/blue]</strong>\nAny 3-Ping grants A2 [red]POD: Shield[/red] and summons POD to launch [red]6[/red] seeker missiles toward random targets in front, dealing Physical DMG and granting [red]POD: Shield[/red] after hitting enemies. Missiles also [red]Taunt[/red] the enemy. (While taunted, the target's DEF is reduced. If 2B and 9S are also in the team, the [red]effect is doubled[/red].) \n- 3-Ping grants A2 POD: Shield equal to [red]5%[/red] of max HP, stacking up to [red]30%[/red] of max HP. \n- Seeker missiles deal [red]140%[/red] Physical DMG in total. \n- Seeker missiles also [red]Taunt[/red] the target, reducing their DEF by [red]20%[/red] for [red]5[/red]s. If 2B and 9S are also in the team, this [red]effect is doubled[/red].\n\n<strong>Sliding — [blue]Moving + Press and hold Dodge[/blue]</strong>\nWhile moving, press and hold the Dodge Button to cause A2 to begin sliding. Gains [red]POD: Shield[/red] after sliding for a period of time. The Dodge Gauge will not recover while sliding, but A2 will emit electricity to [red]continuously pull[/red] nearby enemies. \n- Gains up to [red]10%[/red] of max HP of [red]POD: Shield[/red] during the [red]1st[/red] second of sliding. Sliding lasts up to [red]2[/red]s.",
