                  "description": "Wanshi: Hypnos launches a spinning kick, dealing Physical DMG in a straight line (Ice DMG instead upon a 3-Ping). 1-Ping and 2-Ping grant a short duration of Super Armor while 3-Ping grants a longer duration of Super Armor. \n- Deals [red]170% / 340% / 510%[/red] Physical DMG based on the number of orbs pinged.",
                  "icon": "RED"
