                  "description": "<strong>Basic Attack — [blue]Tap Basic Attack[/blue]</strong>\nAttacks consecutively using the Gunblade, dealing Physical DMG. \n- Deals [red]750%[/red] Physical DMG in total.\n\n<strong>Frost Strike — [blue]Tap Basic Attack[/blue]</strong>\nIn [red]Frost Spirit[/red] form, Basic Attacks are replaced by more powerful [red]Frost Strike[/red] instead, dealing Ice DMG. During the actions of [red]Frost Strike[/red], Chrome: Glory also gains [red]Condensed Frost[/red] for a certain period of time. If Chrome: Glory is attacked during [red]Condensed Frost[/red], the attack will be nullified and the attacker will be slowed, and a certain amount of [red]Glorious Shield[/red] will be restored. [red]Frost Strike[/red] does not recover any Signal Orbs. \n- Deals [red]900%[/red] Ice DMG in total. \n- [red]50%[/red] of [red]Glorious Shield[/red] will be restored if Chrome: Glory is attacked during [red]Condensed Frost[/red].",
