          "memory": "Build:Theatrical_Flame",
          "bio": "A former performer in the Golden Age who is sarcastic on the outside yet serious on the inside. Participated in a lot of actions as an Ascendant. Reformed into the current frame by an agent due to huge damage done to the old frame after a few number of setbacks.",
          "effect": "<strong>Core Passive — [blue]Trigger valid combos[/blue]</strong>\nThe Basic Attack combo DMG ratio is adjusted. Gains [red]Deception Points[/red] based on the combo type upon triggering [red]valid combos[/red]. Roland's Red / Yellow / Blue Orbs are unlocked when there are a certain amount of [red]Deception Points[/red]. Each time the 1st or 2nd hit of a Signal Orb skill is cast, [red]Deception Points[/red] will be consumed to generate Energy. The combos of Basic Attacks and Signal Orb skills can be viewed in the description of each skill. [red]Valid combos[/red]: The Basic Attack combo launched within 1s after dealing DMG from Basic Attacks. Upon triggering Matrix, the next Signal Orb skill cast does not consume any [red]Deception Points[/red] or [red]Trickery Points[/red]. Roland cannot gain Signal Orbs from Basic Attacks. When he is switched off battle, he gains [red]Deception Points[/red]. Signal Orbs gained from any other source would be directly converted into [red]Deception Points[/red] or Energy, prioritizing [red]Deception Points[/red]. \n- The Basic Attack combo DMG ratio changes to [red]200%[/red]. \n- Gains [red]10 / 20 / 30 Deception Points[/red] (up to [red]90[/red]) based on the combo type. \n- Red / Yellow / Blue Orbs are unlocked when there are at least [red]30 Deception Points[/red]. \n- Each time the 1st or 2nd hit of a Signal Orb skill is cast, [red]30 Deception Points[/red] will be consumed to generate [red]10[/red] Energy. \n- Upon triggering Matrix, the next Signal Orb skill cast within [red]10[/red]s does not consume any [red]Deception Points[/red] or [red]Trickery Points[/red]. \n- Gains [red]60 Deception Points[/red] when switched off battle.",
          "priority": "Fire DMG increases by [red]10%[/red]. The cooldown of consecutive dodge is removed. After dodging a damage, accumulates [red]1 Combo 2 - Dazzling Blade[/red], which can be cast directly toward the direction of the joystick by tapping the White Orb. Also increases Extra DMG Bonus by [red]10%[/red] for [red]8s[/red]. During [red]Apex of Trickery[/red], the [red]Deception Points[/red] generated from this combo are converted into [red]10 Trickery Points[/red] instead.",
