                  "name": "Signature: Dream Cosmos Suite",
                  "description": "<strong>Realm of Capriccio — [blue]80 Energy + Tap Signature[/blue]</strong>\nSignature Move: Consumes 80 Energy to activate [red]Realm of Capriccio[/red], gaining Extra DMG Reduction. Selena: Capriccio gains 5 [red]Shooting Stars[/red]. At the end of [red]Realm of Capriccio[/red], all Signal Orbs will be rearranged in the order of Red-Blue-Yellow. \n- Selena: Capriccio's Extra DMG Reduction increases by [red]50%[/red] in Realm of Capriccio.\n\n<strong>Shooting Star — [blue]Ping Shooting Star Orb[/blue]</strong>\nEach time a [red]Shooting Star[/red] is cast, Selena: Capriccio will dash toward the target, dealing Dark DMG.  \n- Deals [red]160%[/red] Dark DMG.\n\n<strong>Reprise: Twin Stars — [blue]All Shooting Star Orbs consumed[/blue]</strong>\nWhen all [red]Shooting Stars[/red] are consumed, Selena: Capriccio will control all phantoms to launch a follow-up attack to cast [red]Reprise: Twin Stars[/red] again, then she will play her Flute Sword to trigger [red]Time Lag Calculation[/red] and order all phantoms to attack the enemy, each phantom dealing Dark DMG. Meanwhile, Realm of Capriccio will be detonated, dealing Dark DMG while leaving a phantom behind, healing ally units within the range every second.  \n- Every phantom deals [red]340%[/red] Dark DMG. \n- The realm explosion deals [red]1360%[/red] Dark DMG in total. \n- The phantom heals ally units within the range for HP equal to [red]30%[/red] of Selena: Capriccio's ATK per second over [red]5[/red]s.",
