                  "name": "Red Orb: Magpie Cut",
                  "description": "<strong>Red Orb — [blue]Ping Red Orb[/blue]</strong>\nAutomatically uses a 3-Ping version of this attack upon switch-in. \nCasts a roundhouse kick that deals Physical DMG. Gains Super Armor upon a 3-Ping. \n- Deals [red]230% / 460% / 690%[/red] Physical DMG based on the number of orbs pinged.\n\n<strong>Dragon Force: Breaking Kick — [blue]25 or more Dragon Force + Ping Red Orb and catch Dragon Axe[/blue]</strong>\nCatching Dragon Axe will consume [red]Dragon Force[/red] to trigger [red]Dragon Force: Breaking Kick[/red]. \n- Casting [red]Dragon Force[/red] Combo will consume [red]25 Dragon Force[/red].",
