                  "description": "<strong>Blue Orb — [blue]Ping Blue Orb[/blue]</strong>\nPerforms kicking strikes that deal Physical DMG. Gains Super Armor upon a 3-Ping. \n- Deals [red]220% / 440% / 660%[/red] Physical DMG based on the number of orbs pinged.\n\n<strong>Dragon Force: Downward Cleave — [blue]25 or more Dragon Force + Ping Blue Orb and catch Dragon Axe[/blue]</strong>\nCatching Dragon Axe will consume [red]Dragon Force[/red] to trigger [red]Dragon Force: Downward Cleave[/red]. \n- Casting [red]Dragon Force[/red] Combo will consume [red]25 Dragon Force[/red].",
                  "icon": "BLU"
