          "memory": "Build:Arca",
          "bio": "The frame that “he” made to save Noan. Initially weighing only 41.3 kg, it was built with many degraded components in order to reduce the user’s movement. Its normal functionality has been ensured after undergoing Babylonia’s improvements.",
          "effect": "<strong>Charge Engine — [blue]Any 3-Ping + Tap Basic Attack repeatedly[/blue]</strong>\nAfter casting a 3-Ping, tap Basic Attack repeatedly to charge up the Rising Engine. When the tapping stops or goes over a certain period of time, Noan: Arca will perform [red]Gear-Break Combo[/red] based on the color of Signal Orbs pinged, and its DMG will depend on the current [red]Gear Level[/red]. Triggering a Combo Strike also consumes all [red]Rising Energy[/red] charged to increase its DMG dealt. The [red]Rising Energy[/red] consumed will be converted into [red]Rotational Speed[/red].\n- Deals [red]150% / 300% / 450% / 600%[/red] Lightning DMG based on the current Gear Level.\n- The Rising Energy charged will increase a Combo Strike's DMG. Each tap increases Base DMG by [red]15%.[/red]\n\n<strong>Gear-Break Combo — [blue]Tap Basic Attack repeatedly to trigger a Combo Strike[/blue]</strong>\nThe next time [red]Gear-Break Combo[/red] is triggered, if the current [red]Rising Energy[/red] exceeds [red]Rotational Speed[/red], [red]Gear Level[/red] will go up by 1.\nWhen Exceed Deduction is triggered, if the progress of [red]sublimation energy[/red] is greater than the [red]target speed[/red] bar, [red]Gear[/red] level will increase by 1.\n\n<strong>Assault-Rising Combo — [blue]Gear Lv.3 + Trigger Combo Strike[/blue]</strong>\nIf [red]Gear-Break Combo[/red] is triggered at Gear Lv. 3, Noan: Arca will perform [red]Assault-Rising Combo[/red] instead with an increased Extra DMG Bonus. [red]Rotational Speed[/red] and [red]Gear Level[/red] will be reset afterward.\n- The Base DMG of [red]Assault-Rising Combo[/red] increases by [red]50%[/red].",
          "priority": "ATK increases by [red]10%[/red]. Triggering [red]Gear-Break Combo[/red] or [red]Assault-Rising Combo[/red] restores [red]10[/red] Signature Energy. Dodge Gauge restores [red]100%[/red] faster.",
