                  "description": "Dashes forward to launch a horizontal slash, followed by an upward thrust that knocks the enemy into the air, dealing Physical DMG.\n— Deals 160% / 320% / 480% Physical DMG in total based on the number of orbs pinged. Deals additional 80% Physical DMG upon a 3-ping.\n— Grants 2 / 3 / 4 Afterglow Points based on the number of orbs pinged.",
