                  "description": "<strong>Strings On Me — [blue]Jete Points + Press and hold Basic Attack[/blue]</strong>\nWhen [red]Jete Points[/red] are greater than [red]0[/red], press and hold Basic Attack to activate [red]Strings On Me[/red] , performing Basic Attacks continuously.\n — [red]Jete Points[/red] increase by [red]40 / 80 / 160[/red] based on the number of orbs pinged.\n — The maximum limit of [red]Jete Points[/red] is [red]160[/red].\n — While [red]Strings On Me[/red] is activated, [red]20 Jete Points[/red] are consumed every [red]0.1[/red]s.\n\n<strong>Solitary Dancer — [blue]Strings On Me + Take Hit/Release Basic Attack[/blue]</strong>\nWhen Bambinata: Vitrum is attacked while [red]Strings On Me[/red] is activated, she will consume all [red]Jete Points[/red] to automatically dodge the attack and leap into the air, entering the [red]Solitary Dancer[/red]. When [red]Strings On Me[/red] is activated at full [red]Jete Points[/red], release the Basic Attack button to consume all [red]Jete Points[/red] and leap up to enter the [red]Solitary Dancer[/red] Form. During the leap, Bambinata: Vitrum dodges incoming attacks. \n\n<strong>Pas De Chat— [blue]Solitary Dancer + Ping[/blue]</strong>\nConsuming Signal Orbs in the [red]Solitary Dancer[/red] Form will trigger [red]Pas De Chat[/red], dealing Ice DMG. During [red]Pas De Chat[/red], Bambinata: Vitrum is invincible and pulls the enemies in. \n — Deals [red]200% / 400% / 600%[/red] Ice DMG based on the number of orbs pinged.\n\n<strong>Pas De Chat— [blue]Successful Dodge + Solitary Dancer + Ping[/blue]</strong>\nIf Bambinata: Vitrum has entered the [red]Solitary Dancer[/red] Form by successfully dodging an attack, pinging Signal Orbs will trigger the more powerful [red]Pas De Chat[/red] that deals Ice DMG. During [red]Pas De Chat[/red], Bambinata: Vitrum is invincible and pulls the enemies in.\n — Deals [red]240% / 480% / 720%[/red] Ice DMG based on the number of orbs pinged.\n\n<strong>Pact of Memory — [blue]Solitary Dancer + 3-Ping[/blue]</strong>\nTriggering [red]Pas De Chat[/red] with a 3-Ping in the [red]Solitary Dancer[/red] Form will grant 1 stack of [red]Pact of Memory[/red] (up to [red]3[/red] stacks), causing Bambinata: Vitrum to forget the color of this 3-Ping and no longer gain orbs of this color. All orbs of this color will be converted to other orbs that have not been forgotten yet. \n— At [red]3[/red] stacks of [red]Pact of Memory[/red], all the remaining orbs will be forgotten and Bambinata can no longer gain Signal Orbs. Casting [red]Signature - Stringless Cage[/red] will remove all stacks of [red]Pact of Memory[/red]  and refund the forgotten orbs. \n— For each [red]1[/red] stack of [red]Pact of Memory[/red], the Base DMG of [red]Signature - Stringless Cage[/red] increases by [red]20%[/red]; up to [red]60%[/red].",
