                  "description": "<strong>Lv. 1— [blue]Unlocked at SS3 Rank[/blue]</strong>\n Gains [red]1[/red] Signal Orb when entering the [red]Solitary Dance[/red] Form via a successful dodge. For every [red]1[/red] stack of [red]Pact of Memory[/red], the Ice DMG of [red]Signature - Stringless Cage[/red] increases by [red]8%[/red]\n\n<strong>Lv. 2 — [blue]Unlocked at SSS Rank[/blue]</strong>\n The [red]Jete Points[/red] consumed every [red]0.1[/red]s during [red] Strings On Me[/red] reduces by [red]50%[/red]. For every [red]1[/red] stack of [red]Pact of Memory[/red], Extra DMG Bonus increases by [red]7%[/red]",
