                  "description": "Automatically uses a 3-Ping version of this attack upon switch-in. \n<strong>Blue Orb — [blue]Kodachi in Hand + Ping Blue Orb[/blue]</strong>\nSlashes the enemy rapidly and deals Lightning DMG.\n— Deals [red]150% / 300% / 450%[/red] Lighting DMG based on the number of orbs pinged.\n— Performing  a Blue Orb 2/3-Ping again will change Alpha's move into jumping up before slashing the enemy, dealing [red]320% / 480%[/red] Lightning DMG.",
