          "weapon": "metis",
          "weaponType": "Halberd Blade",
          "cub": {
              "name": "cetus",
              "notes": "Cetus will leap up, dive to the target location and generate a vortex, dealing DMG and applying Rigidity.\n\nRigidity: Immobilizes the enemy for 2s."
          },
          "memory": "Build: Lost Lullaby",
          "bio": "Lamia's new frame designed by Luna with the Ascendant abilities. Enhanced based on Lamia's old frame, it is capable of switching freely between the human form and the mermaid form. Although Lamia whispered that she wanted a 170cm height, her human form height was only designed to be 169cm.",
          "effect": "<strong>Antinomy</strong>\nWhen Lamia is in [red]Primary Form[/red], she can only cast Yellow or Blue Orb skills, and her Basic Attacks only generate Yellow or Blue Orbs. When she is in [red]Dark Tide Form[/red], she can only cast Red or Blue Orb skills, and her Basic Attacks only generate Red or Blue Orbs. Yellow Orbs will be randomly converted into Red or Blue Orbs.\n\n<strong>Wave Illusions</strong>\nWhen Lamia casts a 3-Ping skill in [red]Primary Form[/red], there is a short window of time in which she can consecutively cast another 3-Ping, [red]Torrent Orb[/red], or [red]Tidal Orb[/red] skill. After Lamia casts a Red Orb skill in [red]Dark Tide Form[/red], consecutively pinging Red Orbs allows her to cast the skill again directly during the skill action. After Lamia casts a Blue Orb skill in [red]Dark Tide Form[/red], she will start swimming in water, during which she can cast the skill again to rapidly fire water spheres to attack the target.\n\n<strong>Drowned Conformation — [blue]Primary Form + Ping Torrent Orb / Tidal Orb[/blue]</strong>\nWhen Lamia casts skills through orb pings in [red]Primary Form[/red], she will gain [red]Fathomless Points[/red]. For every [red]30 Fathomless Points[/red], she will gain a [red]Torrent Orb[/red]. When two [red]Torrent Orbs[/red] are present, they will merge into a [red]Tidal Orb[/red]. At full [red]Fathomless Points[/red], pinging a [red]Torrent Orb[/red] or [red]Tidal Orb[/red] will deplete all [red]Fathomless Points[/red]. When a [red]Torrent Orb[/red] is pinged, Lamia will cast [red]Crushing Wave[/red], dealing Dark DMG to enemies in front while also dealing a small amount DMG to herself. When a [red]Tidal Orb[/red] is pinged, she will cast [red]Suffocating Tide[/red] to pull in surrounding enemies, then detonate the undercurrents to deal Dark DMG. After casting [red]Crushing Wave[/red] or [red]Suffocating Tide[/red], Lamia gains [red]Ocean's Scar[/red]. Pinging a [red]Torrent Orb[/red] will change the weather to [red]Downpour[/red]. Pinging a [red]Tidal Orb[/red] or two [red]Torrent Orbs[/red] will change the weather to [red]Storm[/red]. Lamia gains Super Armor and [red]70%[/red] DMG Reduction while casting [red]Crushing Wave[/red] or [red]Suffocating Tide[/red].\n- [red]Fathomless Points[/red] has a maximum of [red]60[/red].\n- Pinging a [red]Torrent Orb[/red] will cast [red]Crushing Wave[/red], dealing [red]600%[/red] Dark DMG in total.\n- Pinging a [red]Tidal Orb[/red] will cast [red]Suffocating Tide[/red], dealing [red]1300%[/red] Dark DMG in total.\n- Each [red]Torrent Orb[/red] pinged grants [red]25 Abyssal Points[/red] and [red]15[/red] Signature Energy.\n- Each [red]Tidal Orb[/red] pinged grants [red]60 Abyssal Points[/red] and [red]30[/red] Signature Energy.\n\n<strong>Dark Flux — [blue]Dark Tide Form + Ping Torrent Orb / Tidal Orb[/blue]</strong>\nWhen Lamia casts skills through orb pings in [red]Dark Tide Form[/red], she will gain [red]Fathomless Points[/red]. For every [red]30 Fathomless Points[/red], she will gain a [red]Torrent Orb[/red]. When two [red]Torrent Orbs[/red] are present, they will merge into a [red]Tidal Orb[/red]. When [red]Torrent Orb[/red] and [red]Tidal Orb[/red] are both present, the [red]Torrent Orb[/red] will be pinged to enhance [red]Tidal Orb[/red], turning it into [red]Riptide Orb[/red].At full [red]Fathomless Points[/red], pinging a [red]Torrent Orb[/red], [red]Tidal Orb[/red], or [red]Riptide Orb[/red] will deplete all [red]Fathomless Points[/red]. When a [red]Torrent Orb[/red] is pinged, Lamia will cast [red]Crushing Torrent[/red], slashing to create powerful airflows, dealing Dark DMG to enemies in front, and entering [red]Tidal Form[/red]. When a [red]Tidal Orb[/red] or [red]Riptide Orb[/red] is pinged, Lamia will cast [red]Tidal Vortex[/red], dealing Dark DMG. If Lamia is not in [red]Tidal Form[/red] when casting [red]Tidal Vortex[/red], she will ascend to the highest point to cast [red]Tidal Vortex[/red], and then exit [red]Tidal Form[/red].Lamia gains [red]Ocean's Scar[/red] after casting [red]Crushing Torrent[/red] or [red]Tidal Vortex[/red]. Lamia gains Super Armor and [red]70%[/red] DMG Reduction while casting [red]Crushing Torrent[/red] and [red]Tidal Vortex[/red].\n- [red]Fathomless Points[/red] has a maximum of [red]90[/red].\n- Pinging a [red]Torrent Orb[/red] will cast [red]Crushing Torrent[/red], dealing [red]600%[/red] Dark DMG in total.\n- Pinging a [red]Tidal Orb[/red] will cast [red]Tidal Vortex[/red], dealing [red]1300%[/red] Dark DMG in total.\n- Pinging a [red]Riptide Orb[/red] will cast an even more powerful [red]Tidal Vortex[/red], dealing  [red]2200%[/red] Dark DMG in total.\n- Each [red]Torrent Orb[/red] pinged grants [red]25[/red] Abyssal Points and [red]15[/red] Signature Energy.\n- Each [red]Tidal Orb[/red] pinged grants [red]60[/red] Abyssal Points and [red]30[/red] Signature Energy.\n- Each [red]Riptide Orb[/red] pinged grants [red]105[/red] Abyssal Points and [red]35[/red] Signature Energy.",
          "priority": "ATK increases by [red]10%[/red]. The amount of [red]Abyssal Points[/red] earned increases by [red]100%[/red]. Pinging a [red]Tidal Orb[/red] will trigger Matrix if it is not in cooldown.",
