          "memory": "Build:BLACK★ROCK SHOOTER",
          "bio": "A mysterious girl with a blue flame in her left eye and a giant cannon, who has traveled countless worlds.",
          "effect": "<strong>Reflective Nebula</strong>\nWhile performing a Red/Yellow Orb 3-Ping, pinging Red/Yellow Orbs again can interrupt it and recast the skill, dealing DMG based on the number of orbs pinged in the interruption, as well as gaining Blue Orbs equal to the number of orbs pinged when casting [red]Flare Strike[/red] or [red]Starry Bayonet[/red].\n- Blue Orbs are located above the Red/Yellow Orbs and [red]cannot be manually pinged[/red].\n- Blue Orbs cannot be generated through any other source. Basic Attacks can only generate Red / Yellow Orbs.\n- Each Red / Yellow 3-Ping can be interrupted up to [red]2[/red] times.\n- Blue Orbs are still generated if a 3-Ping, [red]Flare Strike[/red], or [red]Starry Bayonet[/red] is interrupted by dodging.\n\n<strong>Limit Released</strong>\nWhile casting [red]Flare Strike[/red] or [red]Starry Bayonet[/red], deals Extra Fire DMG based on the total number of orbs pinged during the entire action sequence (including both the original skill and the recast skill after interruption).\n- Deals one extra hit of DMG for every orb pinged.\n- Each extra hit deals [red]72%[/red] Fire DMG while casting [red]Flare Strike[/red].\n- Each extra hit deals [red]84%[/red] Fire DMG while casting [red]Starry Bayonet[/red].\n\n<strong>Enhanced Blast</strong>\nCasting [red]Basic Attack - Photon Hurricane[/red], [red]Basic Attack - Photon Strike[/red], [red]Basic Attack - Photon Cannon[/red], [red]Astral Edge[/red], and [red]Stellar Cross[/red] will accumulate Blast Energy. When Blast Energy is full, casting [red]Flare Strike[/red] and [red]Starry Bayonet[/red] will deal increased Base DMG.\n- Blast Energy has a maximum value of [red]1000[/red].\n- Each Basic Attack grants [red]14[/red] Blast Energy. Each shot fired in [red]Basic Attack - Photon Strike[/red] grants [red]21[/red] Blast Energy. [red]Basic Attack - Photon Cannon[/red] grants [red]74[/red] Blast Energy.\n-  When casting [red]Astral Edge[/red], [red]Stellar Cross[/red], or when triggering [red]Core Passive - Reflective Nebula[/red], gains [red]100/200/334[/red] Blast Energy based on the number of orbs pinged.\n- When Blast Energy is full, casting [red]Flare Strike[/red] or [red]Starry Bayonet[/red] will deplete the Blast Energy and increase the Base DMG of [red]Flare Strike[/red] or [red]Starry Bayonet[/red] by [red]100%[/red].",
