                  "name": "Red Orb: Astral Edge - Ping Red Orb",
                  "description": "Automatically uses a 3-Ping version of this attack upon switch-in. \nQuickly slashes forward multiple times, dealing Fire DMG in a large area. Upon a 3-Ping, automatically follows up with [red]Flare Strike[/red], dealing Extra Fire DMG.\n- Deals [red]75% / 150% / 225%[/red] Fire DMG in total based on the number of orbs pinged.\n- [red]Flare Strike[/red] deals [red]250%[/red] Fire DMG.\n- Gains Super Armor and [red]70%[/red] DMG Reduction while casting [red]Flare Strike[/red].",
