                  "description": "<strong>Burst Drive — [blue]10 Signature Energy + Tap Signature[/blue]</strong>\nUnleashes a powerful thrust toward the target in front, dealing Fire DMG and activating [red]Azure Awakening[/red]. Becomes invincible when casting [red]Signature - Burst Drive[/red].\n- Deals [red]200%[/red] Fire DMG.\n- Fire DMG increases by [red]15%[/red] in [red]Azure Awakening[/red].\n- [red]Azure Awakening[/red] lasts [red]10s[/red].\n\n<strong>Ethereal Star — [blue]Azure Awakening + Blue Orbs available + Press and hold/tap Signature[/blue]</strong>\nCharges the Rock Cannon and automatically consumes all [red]Entangled Hearts[/red] and Signature Energy to fire a powerful blast toward the target area, dealing Fire DMG and exiting [red]Azure Awakening[/red].\n- Deals [red]700%[/red] Fire DMG in total. Becomes Invincible when casting [red]Signature - Ethereal Star[/red].\n- [red]Signature - Ethereal Star[/red] cannot be cast while casting [red]Flare Strike, Starry Bayonet[/red], or [red]Basic Attack - Skycrushing Blade[/red].",
