          "memory": "Build:Epitaph",
          "bio": "A frame independently developed by the Forsaken for tough battles with a brand-new design of the M.I.N.D. carrier module.",
          "effect": "<strong>Composite Structure</strong>\nUnder [red]Patrol Mode[/red], Watanabe can only use Yellow or Blue Orbs, and his Basic Attacks only generate Yellow or Blue Orbs. When [red]Assault Mode[/red] is activated, he can only use Red and [red]Blaze Orbs[/red], and his Basic Attacks only generate Red Orbs.\n\n<strong>Engine Optimization — [blue]Any 3-Ping or upon entering Matrix[/blue]</strong>\nAfter any 3-Ping, Watanabe: Epitaph gains [red]1 Shotshell[/red], up to 3. Upon entering Matrix, he gains 1 [red]Blaze Orb[/red]. He may have up to [red]3 Blaze Orbs[/red] at the same time, and excess [red]Blaze Orbs[/red] will be converted into random Signal Orbs.\n\n<strong>Fire Walker — [blue]Assault Mode + Press and hold Dodge[/blue]</strong>\nUses the grappling hook to pull in the target from a distance, dealing Fire DMG. If the target cannot be pulled, Watanabe: Epitaph will dash toward the target instead. Gains Super Armor and [red]40%[/red] DMG Reduction while casting this skill. Using Basic Attack or Red Orb skill during the pulling action immediately triggers [red]Parry[/red].\n- Deals [red]40%[/red] Fire DMG in total.\n\n<strong>Resilient Strike — [blue]Trigger Parry[/blue]</strong>\nUpon [red]Parry[/red], triggers [red]Fortified Shield[/red] that grants a Shield equal to [red]30%[/red] of Max HP, deals Fire DMG, and inflicts [red]Scorching Invasion[/red] that reduces the target's Fire Resistance. Triggering [red]Fortified Shield[/red] again will replenish the Shield capacity. Enters Matrix if it is not on cooldown when [red]Fortified Shield[/red] is triggered.\n- Deals [red]360%[/red] Fire DMG in total. [red]Scorching Invasion[/red] reduces the target’s Fire Resistance by [red]25%[/red] for [red]8s[/red].\n\n<strong>Scorching Torrent — [blue]Assault Mode + Have 3 Shotshells + Press and hold Basic Attack[/blue]</strong>\nUses the grappling hook to glide around and descends from above, consuming [red]3[/red] Shotshells to pull in nearby enemy units and deal Fire DMG. While casting [red]Scorching Torrent[/red], Watanabe becomes invincible but is unable to cast [red]Signature - Explosive Purge[/red]. Gains [red]12[/red] Signature Energy after casting.\n- Deals [red]1350%[/red] Fire DMG in total.",
          "priority": "ATK increases by 10%. Upon entering the [red]Assault Mode[/red], gains 3 Red Orbs, up to 6 orbs each time when entering the battlefield. Can quickly cast [red]Scorching Torrent[/red] after pinging Red Orbs.",
