          "memory": "Build:Shukra",
          "bio": "A frame reforged by Tabula Akasha through life and death even with the Transcendant's Punishing Virus removed. Its principle and structure remain unknown.",
          "effect": "<strong>Whisper Breaker — [blue]Any 3 Ping + Any Orb Ping[/blue]</strong>\nAfter a 3-Ping, pings any Signal Orb immediately to cast [red]Tabula Akasha - Engrave[/red] and summons Huiyu to attack the target, gaining Super Armor and [red]70%[/red] DMG Reduction, rearranging Signal Orbs into 3-Ping sets, entering [red]Into the Fray[/red], and gaining 1 [red]Inscription[/red] and 1 Signal Orb during so. During [red]Into the Fray[/red], any 3-Ping will grant [red]Inscription[/red], and Huiyu will deal Extra Ice DMG upon a 3-Ping or the 4th-or-5th hit of the Basic Attack.\n- Deals [red]200% / 400% / 600%[/red] Ice DMG in total based on the number of orbs pinged when summoning Huiyu.\n- Huiyu performs a follow-up attack and deals [red]140% / 130% / 140%[/red] Ice DMG upon a Red/Yellow/Blue 3-Ping.\n- Huiyu performs a follow-up attack and deals [red]140% /180%[/red] Ice DMG upon the 4th/5th hit of the Basic Attack.\n- Pings orbs during the Entrance Skill to enter [red]Into the Fray[/red] immediately.\n- [red]Into the Fray[/red] lasts for [red]8[/red]s. Gains up to 3 [red]Inscription[/red] during so. \n\n<strong>Sun Rider</strong>\nUpon entering a Matrix she has triggered, Qu: Shukra activates [red]Sunshift[/red] for 4s. Gains [red]20[/red] Signature Energy every time she is switched in.\n\n<strong>Will Bearer — [blue]Into the Fray + During Sunshift + Press and Hold Dodge[/blue]</strong>\nImmediately exits [red]Into the Fray[/red] and converts all [red]Inscription[/red] to [red]Glyphs[/red]. Qu: Shukra pulls in enemy units and summons feathers to continue attacking the target, dealing Ice DMG and gaining Signature Energy continuously. Qu: Shukra is Invincible during so. The next [red]Enlightened Soul[/red] cast is enhanced.\n- Deals [red]1870%[/red] Ice DMG in total.\n- Each attack grants [red]3[/red] Signature Energy. \n- For the next cast of [red]Enlightened Soul[/red], every 3-Ping grants [red]2 stacks of Soul Ripples[/red] during [red]Enthronement[/red]. This effect does not stack with the enhancement to [red]Sovereign's Presence[/red] triggered by [red]Mountain Caller[/red].\n\n <strong>Snow Drifter — [blue] Into the Fray + Inscription Not Full + Press and Hold Basic Attack[/blue]</strong>\nQu: Shukra assumes her sword stance and becomes Invincible briefly before dashing toward her target and leaping into the air, striking the target and dealing Ice DMG. Gains Super Armor and [red]50%[/red] DMG Reduction during this skill.\n- Deals [red]1600%[/red] Ice DMG in total. \n- Automatically dodges during the dash.\n\n<strong>Mountain Caller — [blue]Into the Fray + Inscription Full + Press and Hold Basic Attack[/blue]</strong>\nImmediately exits [red]Into the Fray[/red] and converts all [red]Inscription[/red] to [red]Glyphs[/red]. Qu: Shukra summons an ice mountain that freezes the target briefly before she shatters the mountain, pulling in enemy units, dealing Ice DMG, and gaining Signature Energy continuously. Qu: Shukra is Invincible during so. The next [red]Sovereign's Presence[/red] cast is enhanced.\n- Deals [red]2000%[/red] Ice DMG in total.\n- Each attack grants [red]4[/red] Signature Energy.\n-For the next cast of [red]Sovereign's Presence[/red], doubles the Base DMG increase on [red]Sovereign's Presence[/red] from consuming [red]Soul Ripples[/red]. This effect does not stack with the enhancement to [red]Enlightened Soul[/red] triggered by [red]Will Bearer[/red].",
          "priority": "ATK increases by 10%. Upon activating Into the Fray, triggers Matrix if it is not in cooldown and grants a bonus Inscription. When casting Mountain Caller, each attack grants 3 extra Signature Energy.",
