                  "name": "Basic Attack: Tabula Akasha",
                  "description": "<strong>Tabula Akasha - Scribe — [blue]Tap Basic Attack[/blue]</strong>\nStrikes the enemy with her Longsword, dealing Ice DMG.\n- Deals [red]670%[/red] Ice DMG in total.\n\n<strong>Tabula Akasha - Engrave — [blue]Into the Fray + Any 3-Ping + Tap Basic Attack[/blue]</strong>\nPerforms an extra hit of follow-up attack, dealing Ice DMG. Gains Signature Energy and extends the duration of [red]Into the Fray[/red].\n- The follow-up attack deals [red]420%[/red] Ice DMG upon a 3-Ping.\n-The duration of Into the Fray extends by [red]0.5[/red]s, up to [red]8[/red]s.\n- Gains [red]3[/red] Signature Energy.",
