              {
                  "name": "SSS+ Rank: Chronicle's Apex",
                  "description": "<strong>Lv. 1 — [blue]Unlocked at SSS3 Rank[/blue]</strong>\nExtra DMG Bonus of [red]Will Bearer[/red], [red]Snow Drifter[/red], and [red]Mountain Caller[/red] increases by [red]50%[/red].\n\n<strong>Lv. 2 — [blue]Unlocked at SSS6 Rank[/blue]</strong>\nExtra DMG Bonus of 3-Ping skills, [red]Tabula Akasha - Engrave[/red], and [red]Enlightened Soul[/red] increases by [red]50%[/red].\n\n<strong>Lv. 3 — [blue]Unlocked at SSS+ Rank[/blue]</strong>\nExtra DMG Bonus of [red]Sovereign's Presence[/red] increases by [red]45%[/red].",
                  "icon": "SSS"
              }
