          "memory": "Build:Oblivion",
          "bio": "Once an agent of the Ascension-Network, she now seeks to resist, guide, and control the entire Ascension-Network to create an ideal paradise after the Agent Zero incident.",
          "effect": "<strong>Waxing Course</strong>\n\nEnters [red]Nova[/red] upon entering the battlefield. When in [red]Nova[/red], all Signal Orbs will be converted into Yellow Orbs,\nand Basic Attacks will only generate Yellow Orbs. After entering [red]Main Sequence[/red], all Signal Orbs will be\nconverted into Red and Blue Orbs, and Basic Attacks will only generate Red or Blue Orbs. After entering\n[red]Finality[/red], Basic Attacks will not generate Signal Orbs, and no Signal Orbs can be pinged except for [red]Finality Orbs[/red].\n\n<strong>Eclipse Points – [blue]Gained automatically when casting Signal Orb Skills / casting Shattering Moon at max Crescent Points[/blue]</strong>\n\nGains [red]Eclipse Points[/red] whenever casting Signal Orb Skills, or casting [red]Shattering Moon[/red] or [red]Incipient Retribution[/red] at max [red]Crescent Points[/red]. [red]Eclipse Points[/red] will amplify the Base DMG of [red]Signature - Lunar Downfall[/red] in [red]Main Sequence[/red] and the Base DMG of [red]Final Retribution[/red] in [red]Finality[/red].\n\n- Gains [red]5 / 10 / 15 Eclipse Points[/red] based on the number of orbs pinged.\n\n- Gains [red]45 Eclipse Points[/red] upon casting [red]Shattering Moon[/red] or [red]Incipient Retribution[/red] at max [red]Crescent Points[/red].\n\n- Can gain up to [red]300 Eclipse Points[/red].\n\n<strong>Incipient Retribution — [blue]Main Sequence + Activated Eclipse Stance + Reaping Moon + Release Basic Attack[/blue]</strong>\n\nWhen in [red]Main Sequence[/red] with [red]Eclipse Stance[/red] activated, release Basic Attack during [red]Reaping Moon[/red] to cast [red]Incipient Retribution[/red]. Upon casting, Luna: Oblivion gathers energy and charges toward the target to pull in nearby enemies and detonate them, dealing Nihil DMG and restoring [red]24[/red] Signature Energy. She becomes invincible during so, unable to restore the Dodge Gauge or cast [red]Signature - Lunar Downfall[/red].\n\n- When [red]Crescent Points[/red] are not full, [red]Incipient Retribution[/red] deals [red]1500%[/red] Nihil DMG.\n\n- When cast at max [red]Crescent Points[/red], [red]Incipient Retribution[/red] grants [red]45 Eclipse Points[/red], deals [red]3000%[/red] Nihil DMG, and clears all [red]Crescent Points[/red].\n\n- Casts [red]Incipient Retritbution[/red] automatically at max Crescent Points\n\n<strong>Final Retribution – [blue]Finality + Activated Eclipse Stance + Press and Hold Basic Attack[/blue]</strong>\nWhen in [red]Finality[/red] with [red]Eclipse Stance[/red] activated, press and hold Basic Attack to cast [red]Final Retribution[/red]. Upon casting, Luna: Oblivion gathers energy and charges toward the target to pull in nearby enemies and detonate them, dealing Nihil DMG and amplifying this damage at the cost of all [red]Eclipse Points[/red]. She becomes invincible during so, unable to restore the Dodge Gauge or cast [red]Signature - Lunar Downfall[/red].\n\n- [red]Final Retribution[/red] deals [red]3800%[/red] Nihil DMG. Every [red]10 Eclipse Points[/red] will amplify Base DMG by [red]4%[/red].\n\n<strong>Serene Advent – [blue]Cast Signature - Finality[/blue]</strong>\n\nWhen in [red]Finality[/red], Luna: Oblivion consumes [red]Crescent Points[/red] continuously but is unable to gain them back through [red]Reaping Moon[/red]. Gains [red]Finality Orbs[/red] upon Basic Attacks; restores [red]30 Crescent Points[/red] and gains 3 [red]Finality Orbs[/red] upon casting [red]Shattering Moon[/red]. When the number of [red]Crescent Points[/red] falls to 0, exits [red]Finality[/red], and all [red]Finality Orbs[/red] will disappear.\n\n- In [red]Finality[/red], expends [red]10 Crescent Points[/red] per second.\n\n- Casts [red]Void Dissipation[/red] upon pinging a [red]Finality Orb[/red], dealing [red]400%[/red] Nihil DMG, restoring [red]12[/red] Signature Energy and [red]20 Crescent Points[/red]. When [red]Eclipse Stance[/red] is activated, gains additional [red]15 Eclipse Points[/red].\n\n<strong>Agitated Beacon</strong>\nWhen in [red]Main Sequence / Finality[/red], Luna: Oblivion's Base DMG Efficiency dealt to Equilibrium Field increases by [red]100%[/red].",
