                  "description": "<strong>Lv. 1 — [blue]Unlocked at S5 Rank[/blue]</strong>\n Casting [red]Basic Attack - Aura Blast/Basic Attack - Aura Dance/Signature - Crowd Slash/Signature - Eclipse Daybreak[/red] will activate all available QTEs.\n\n <strong>Lv. 2 — [blue]Unlocked at SS Rank[/blue]</strong>\n Gains a [red]25%[/red] Extra DMG Bonus during the [red]Fire Thunder Form[/red] or [red]when airborne[/red]. Immediately gains [red]120 Aura Value[/red] upon becoming [red]airborne[/red]. When exiting the battlefield after casting [red]Signature: Eclipse Daybreak[/red], Lucia will enter the [red]Flickering Ember[/red] status and launch an attack at nearby enemies every [red]2[/red]s, dealing [red]4000%[/red] Fire DMG. Lucia will exit the [red]Flickering Ember[/red] status after 4 attacks.",
