              {
                  "name": "Red Orb: Thunderflare Storm",
                  "description": "<strong>Red Orb Combo 1 —  [blue]Not in Red Orb Combo + Tap Red Orb[/blue]</strong>\nStartrail performs a spinning slash attack and enters the [red]Red Orb Combo[/red], dealing Lightning DMG and applying a [red]Thunderflare Mark[/red] on hit. The [red]Thunderflare Mark[/red] explodes after [red]0.7[/red]s, dealing Lightning DMG. If a [red]Thunderflare Mark[/red] already exists when this skill is cast, it will detonate immediately, creating a shockwave that deals damage to the user.\n- The slash attack deals [red]100%[/red] Lightning DMG. The [red]Thunderflare Mark[/red] explosion deals [red]100%[/red] Lightning DMG.\n- If hit while casting this skill, blocks with a shield and gains [red]1[/red] stack of [red]Crystal Field[/red], up to a maximum of [red]2[/red] stacks.\n- If the target has a [red]Thunderflare Mark[/red] when this skill is cast, the [red]Thunderflare Mark[/red] will detonate immediately and block the shockwave, gaining an extra [red]1[/red] stack of [red]Crystal Field[/red], up to a maximum of [red]2[/red] stacks.\n\n<strong>Red Orb Combo 2 — [blue]In Red Orb Combo + Ping Red Orb[/blue]</strong>\nLeaps and performs a downward slash, dealing Lightning DMG and gaining [red]Starlight Points[/red].\n- Deals [red]220% / 440% / 660%[/red] Lightning DMG and gains [red]15 / 30 / 50 Starlight Points[/red], based on the number of orbs pinged, up to a maximum of [red]100[/red] points.",
                  "icon": "RED"
              },
              {
                  "name": "Yellow Orb: Starbeam Deconstruction",
                  "description": "<strong>Aetherstrike — [blue]Sword Shield in Hand + At Least 50 Starlight Points + Tap Yellow Orb[/blue]</strong>\nSpins to attack enemies, combining the weapon into a [red]Shield Axe[/red]. Gains Super Armor and DMG Reduction during the attack, dealing Lightning DMG and clearing the [red]Blazing Mark[/red].\n- Deals [red]950%[/red] Lightning DMG and grants Super Armor and [red]80%[/red] DMG Reduction while casting.\n\n<strong>Prismatic Thrust — [blue]Shield Axe in Hand + Tap Yellow Orb[/blue]</strong>\nSprints and attacks enemies, splitting the [red]Shield Axe[/red] into a [red]Sword Shield[/red], dealing Lightning DMG while gaining Super Armor.\n- Deals [red]150%[/red] Lightning DMG.\n\n<strong>Inferno Cyclone — [blue]Sword Shield in Hand + At Least 50 Starlight Points + Press and Hold Yellow Orb[/blue]</strong>\nImmediately combines the [red]Sword Shield[/red] into a [red]Shield Axe[/red] and continuously attacks enemies while consuming [red]Starlight Points[/red]. Pulls enemies together and deals Ignition DMG, applying [red]Combustible Charge[/red], gaining a [red]Blazing Mark[/red] and Signature Energy. While this skill is cast, gains Super Armor and DMG Reduction, and cannot cast [red]Decisive Detonation![/red].\n- Continuously consumes up to [red]100 Starlight Points[/red] each time, dealing [red]4000%[/red] Ignition DMG in total, applying [red]5000 Combustible Charge[/red], and gaining [red]60[/red] Signature Energy. While this skill is cast, gains Super Armor and [red]70%[/red] DMG Reduction.\n- Releasing Yellow Orb prematurely will immediately trigger [red]Blazing Rift[/red]. \n-  [red]Blazing Mark[/red] lasts [red]10[/red] seconds. Duration resets every time the effect is triggered.",
                  "icon": "YEL"
              },
              {
                  "name": "Blue Orb: Comet Burst",
                  "description": "<strong>Blue Orb Combo 1 — [blue]Not in Blue Orb Combo + Tap Blue Orb[/blue]</strong>\nStartrail performs a sprint attack and enters the [red]Blue Orb Combo[/red], dealing Lightning DMG and applying a [red]Thunderflare Mark[/red] on hit. The Thunderflare Mark explodes after [red]0.7[/red]s, dealing Lightning DMG. If a Thunderflare Mark already exists when this skill is cast, it will detonate immediately, creating a shockwave that deals damage to the user.\n- The sprint attack deals [red]100%[/red] Lightning DMG. [red]Glaring Flashmark[/red] deals [red]100%[/red] Lightning DMG when it explodes.\n-  If hit while using this skill, block with a shield and gain [red]1[/red] stack of [red]Crystal Field[/red], up to a maximum of [red]2[/red] stacks.\n- If the target has a [red]Thunderflare Mark[/red] when this skill is cast, the [red]Thunderflare Mark[/red] will detonate immediately and block the shockwave, gaining an extra [red]1[/red] stack of [red]Crystal Field[/red], up to a maximum of [red]2[/red] stacks.\n\n<strong>Blue Orb Combo 2 — [blue]In Blue Orb combo + Ping Blue Orb[/blue]</strong>\nTurns and chops the enemy, dealing Lightning DMG and gaining [red]Starshine Points[/red].\n- Deals [red]220% / 440% / 660%[/red] Lightning DMG and gains [red]15 / 30 / 50 Starshine Points[/red], accumulating up to a maximum of [red]100[/red] points based on the number of orbs pinged.",
                  "icon": "BLU"
              },
              {
                  "name": "Basic Attack: Radiant Surge",
                  "description": "<strong>Wandering Starburst — [blue]Sword Shield in Hand + Tap Basic Attack[/blue]</strong>\nPerform alternating attacks with the [red]Sword Shield[/red], dealing a total of [red]510%[/red] Lightning DMG.\n\n<strong>Thunder Vortex — [blue]Shield Axe in Hand + Tap Basic Attack[/blue]</strong>\nAttacks with the [red]Shield Axe[/red], dealing Lightning DMG. If there are sufficient [red]Starlight Points[/red], consuming them during the attack will grant [red]Overload[/red], dealing Lightning DMG while granting Super Armor and DMG Reduction.\n- Deals a total of [red]680%[/red] Lightning DMG.\n- If there are sufficient [red]Starlight Points[/red], extra [red]Flowing Light[/red] will be released. Each attack consumes [red]10 / 25 / 30 / 35 Starlight Points[/red], granting [red]30 / 75 / 90 / 105 Overload[/red] and [red]3 / 7 / 9 / 11[/red] Signature Energy, and deals an extra [red]400% / 1100% / 2100% / 2600%[/red] Lightning DMG while granting Super Armor and [red]60%[/red] DMG Reduction. The maximum [red]Overload[/red] is [red]300[/red] points.",
                  "icon": "BAS"
              },
              {
                  "name": "Signature: Decisive Detonation!",
                  "description": "<strong>Cosmic Starstrike — [blue]80 Signature Energy + Sword Shield in Hand + Tap Signature[/blue]</strong>\nCombines the weapon into a Shield Axe and performs a slash on enemies, dealing damage. During the attack, [red]Time Lag Calculation[/red] is triggered, and the weapon automatically switches back to the Sword Shield after the attack. If the [red]Field Ultralimit[/red] effect is active when casting this skill, its duration is refreshed.\n- Deals a total of [red]4000%[/red] Lightning DMG.\n- If the [red]Blazing Mark[/red] is active when casting this skill, the [red]Blazing Mark[/red] will be cleared, and [red]Cosmic Starstrike: Burn[/red] will be cast instead. Turns [red]Combustible state[/red] into [red]Ignition state[/red] of equal stacks, dealing [red]4000%[/red] Ignition DMG. Gains the [red]Ember Mark[/red] for [red]15[/red]s.\n- If the [red]Ember Mark[/red] is active upon leaving the battle, the mark's duration is refreshed to 15s. Duration resets every time the effect is triggered.\n\n<strong>Starshard Slash — [blue]80 Signature Energy + Shield Axe in Hand + Tap Signature[/blue]</strong>\nAttack enemies with the Shield Axe, dealing [red]4000%[/red] Lightning DMG. During the attack, [red]Time Lag Calculation[/red] is triggered, and the weapon automatically switches back to the Sword Shield after the attack. If the [red]Field Ultralimit[/red] effect is active when casting this skill, its duration is reset.\n\n<strong>Thunderfire Domain</strong>\nAfter casting [red]Cosmic Starstrike[/red] or [red]Starshard Slash[/red], a domain is left behind, dealing continuous damage and weakening enemies.\n- The domain deals [red]50%[/red] Lightning DMG per second for [red]12[/red]s. Duration resets every time it is triggered.\n- If the [red]Blazing Mark[/red] is active when casting this skill, the domain will instead deal [red]50%[/red] Ignition DMG per second for [red]12[/red]s. Duration resets every time it is triggered.",
                  "icon": "SIG"
              },
              {
                  "name": "QTE: Orbital Interference",
                  "description": "Deals damage and weakens enemies.\n- Deals [red]300%[/red] Lightning DMG upon the first hit and applies a [red]Turbulence Interference[/red] effect that reduces Lightning Resistance by [red]25%[/red] for [red]8[/red]s. Deals [red]50%[/red] Lightning DMG per second for the following 8s.\n-  If the [red]Ember Mark[/red] is active when casting this skill, it will instead deal [red]300%[/red] Ignition DMG upon the first hit and apply a [red]Scorching Invasion[/red] effect that reduces Fire Resistance by [red]25%[/red] for [red]8[/red]s. Deals [red]50%[/red] Ignition DMG per second for the following 8s.",
                  "icon": "QTE"
              },
              {
                  "name": "Core Passive: Astral Armament",
                  "description": "<strong>Meteoric Doom — [blue]Shield Axe in Hand + At Least 100 points of Overload or Starlight + Press and Hold Basic Attack[/blue]</strong>\nConsumes all [red]Overload[/red] and [red]Starlight Points[/red] to cast [red]Meteoric Doom[/red], pulling nearby enemies and triggering Matrix if it is not on cooldown. Becomes [red]Invincible[/red] while casting and it is not allowed to cast [red]Decisive Detonation![/red]. Deals Lightning DMG and grants Signature Energy.\n- Deals a total of [red]3800%[/red] Lightning DMG and gains [red]30[/red] Signature Energy.\n- Consumes all [red]Starlight Points[/red] when this skill is cast, converting them into an equal amount of [red]Overload[/red].\n- For every [red]15[/red] points of [red]Overload[/red] consumed, the Base DMG of this [red]Meteoric Doom[/red] increases by [red]3%[/red].\n\n<strong>Blazing Rift — [blue]During Inferno Cyclone + Release Yellow Orb or Starlight Points are depleted During Inferno Cyclone[/blue]</strong>\nImmediately switches the weapon to the [red]Sword Shield[/red], dealing Ignition DMG and triggering Matrix if it is not on cooldown. Gains Super Armor and DMG Reduction while this skill is cast. Upon first casting, gains an enhanced effect.\n- Deals a total of [red]700%[/red] Ignition DMG.  Gains Super Armor and [red]80%[/red] DMG Reduction while this skill is cast.\n- Upon first casting, [red]Blazing Rift[/red] is enhanced, granting [red]12[/red] Signature Energy. Additionally, for each [red]5 Starlight Points[/red] consumed by [red]Inferno Cyclone[/red], the Base DMG of [red]Blazing Rift[/red] increases by [red]10%[/red]. After casting [red]Decisive Detonation![/red], the next [red]Blazing Rift[/red] will be granted an enhanced effect again.\n\n<strong>Structural Meltdown</strong>\nWhen Startrail deals damage using the [red]Shield Axe[/red], enemies will be weakened.\n- Applies a [red]Turbulence Interference[/red] effect to enemies, reducing their Lightning Resistance by [red]25%[/red] for [red]2[/red]s.\n-  If a [red]Blazing Mark[/red] is active when dealing damage, it will instead apply a [red]Scorching Invasion[/red] effect to enemies, reducing their Fire Resistance by [red]25%[/red] for [red]2[/red]s.\n\n<strong>Hyper Mecha</strong>\nWhen Startrail switches to the Shield Axe, gains a Shield equal to [red]30%[/red] of the maximum HP. The Shield is removed when switching back to the Sword Shield. Upon entering battle each time, gains a Signal Orb.\n\n<strong>Effect: Ignition</strong>\nCombustible: Every [red]250[/red] Combustible Charges will add [red]1[/red] Combustible stack, up to 20 stacks.\nIgnition: Ignited units take Ignition DMG equal to [red]Ignition stacks x30%[/red] (Tank Skills will not be triggered) every second for 10s.\n- The subsequent unit will inherit the Combustible/Ignition status of the last unit on the battlefield upon its death.",
                  "icon": "COR"
              },
              {
                  "name": "Leader: Astral Beacon",
                  "description": "Increases Lightning DMG and Ignition DMG of all members by [red]10%[/red]. Increases DMG of all Tank Omniframes in the team by [red]5%[/red].",
                  "icon": "LEA"
              },
              {
                  "name": "SS Rank: Quantum Beat",
                  "description": "<strong>Lv. 1 — [blue]Unlocked at S5 Rank[/blue]</strong>\nSwitching to the Shield Axe and casting [red]Meteoric Doom[/red], [red]Blazing Rift[/red], [red]Cosmic Starstrike[/red], or [red]Starshard Slash[/red] will activate all available QTEs.\n\n<strong>Lv. 2 — [blue]Unlocked at SS Rank[/blue]</strong>\nAutomatically uses a QTE when exiting the battle. After casting [red]Red/Blue Orb Combo 2[/red], tapping on the Red/Blue Orb again will directly cast the corresponding Combo 2. [red]Aetherstrike[/red] and [red]Red/Blue Orb Combo 2[/red] Base DMG increase by [red]60%[/red]. [red]Flowing Light[/red] Base DMG increases by [red]100%[/red]. [red]Inferno Cyclone[/red] Base DMG increases by [red]110%[/red]. If [red]Meteoric Doom[/red] is cast and consumes [red]100[/red] points of [red]Starlight[/red], gains [red]50[/red] extra points of [red]Overload[/red]. This instance of [red]Meteoric Doom[/red] increases its Base DMG by [red]50%[/red]. Gains [red]15[/red] Signature Energy the first time Shield Axe is switched on upon entering the battle.",
                  "icon": "SS"
              },
              {
                  "name": "SSS Rank: Blazing Shooting Star",
                  "description": "<strong>Lv. 1 — [blue]Unlocked at SS3 Rank[/blue]</strong>\nResistance Reduction of [red]Turbulence Interference[/red] and [red]Scorching Invasion[/red] increases by [red]10%[/red]. Base DMG of [red]Meteoric Doom[/red] increases by [red]100%[/red], and Base DMG of [red]Blazing Rift[/red] increases by [red]60%[/red]. [red]Inferno Cyclone[/red] applies [red]Combustible Charge 100%[/red] faster.\n\n<strong>Lv. 2 — [blue]Unlocked at SSS Rank[/blue]</strong>\nResistance Reduction of [red]Turbulence Interference[/red] and [red]Scorching Invasion[/red] increases by [red]10%[/red]. Each time [red]Meteoric Doom[/red] consumes [red]75[/red] points of [red]Overload[/red], the next casting of [red]Starshard Slash[/red] increases its Base DMG by [red]25%[/red]. Stacks are cleared when separating the Shield Axe. For each [red]5[/red] stacks of [red]Combustible[/red] on the target, casting [red]Cosmic Starstrike: Burn[/red] increases its Base DMG by [red]16%[/red]. Upon entering the battle, casting [red]Decisive Detonation![/red] for the first time grants [red]100[/red] points of [red]Starlight[/red]. The phase 4 of the first [red]Flowing Light[/red] cast grants [red]16[/red] extra points of Signature Energy. Cooldown time for switching between all characters in the team reduces by [red]3[/red]s. This effect does not stack with other effects of the same type.",
                  "icon": "SSS"
              },
              {
                  "name": "SSS+ Rank: Starforge Core",
                  "description": "<strong>Lv. 1 — [blue]Unlocked at SSS3 Rank[/blue]</strong>\nExtra DMG of [red]Meteoric Doom[/red], [red]Flowing Light[/red], and [red]Blazing Rift[/red] increases by [red]20%[/red], [red]35%[/red], and [red]100%[/red] respectively.\n\n<strong>Lv. 2 — [blue]Unlocked at SSS6 Rank[/blue]</strong>\nExtra DMG of [red]Aetherstrike[/red] and [red]Red/Blue Orb Combo 2[/red] increases by [red]100%[/red]. Extra DMG of [red]Inferno Cyclone[/red] increases by [red]50%[/red]. \n\n<strong>Lv. 3 — [blue]Unlocked at SSS+ Rank[/blue]</strong>\nExtra DMG of [red]Cosmic Starstrike[/red] and [red]Starshard Slash[/red] increases by [red]40%[/red].",
                  "icon": "SSS"
              }
