          "memory": "Build:Parhelion",
          "bio": "Along with the rise and fall of countless civilizations, this is where Ishmael's choices intersect. This frame was born from a cosmos beyond time with materials beyond human comprehension, as enigmatic as the will of the Observer that operates within.",
          "effect": "<strong>Observation Notes</strong> \n Ishmael: Parhelion determines her ability based on [red]Observation Notes[/red]. [red]Observation Notes[/red]' ability will [red]be enhanced along with the appearance of other Constructs[/red]. \n - When there's only one elemental Tank on team, Ishmael: Parhelion will become the Amplifier of that element. \n - When there's only one elemental Support/Amplifier, she will become the Tank of that element.\n\n<strong>Parhelion Arc</strong> \nWhen Ishmael: Parhelion is in the [red]Wanderer Form[/red], all Signal Orbs will turn into Blue Orbs. When she's in the [red]Dominator Form[/red], all Signal Orbs will become Red Orbs.\n\n<strong>Mirage Phantom: [blue]Tap Dodge Repeatedly[/blue]</strong> \nCasts projection to deal Nihil DMG when dodging. Tap Dodge repeatedly to cast [red]Phantom Orbit[/red]. When in the [red]Dominator Form[/red], casts [red]Phantom Annihilation[/red] at the cost of [red]30 Phantom Points[/red], dealing Nihil DMG. [red]Phantom Annihilation[/red] will deal more damage, restore [red]Signature Energy[/red], and not consume Dodge Gauge value. Gains the [red]Collapse Mark[/red] after casting the 5th hit of [red]Phantom Annihilation[/red]. \n - Casts projection to deal [red]80%[/red] Nihil DMG when dodging. \n - [red]Phantom Points[/red] are capped at [red]150[/red]. \n - Casting [red]Phantom Orbit[/red] in the [red]Wanderer Form[/red] will deal [red]100% / 120% / 120%  / 180% / 250%[/red] Nihil DMG. \n - Casting [red]Phantom Orbit[/red] in the [red]Dominator Form[/red] will pull in nearby enemy units and deal [red]180% / 270% / 330% / 300% / 430%[/red] Nihil DMG. \n - Casting [red]Phantom Annihilation[/red] in the [red]Dominator Form[/red] will pull in nearby enemy units, deal [red]660% / 990% / 1210% / 1100% / 1540%[/red] Nihil DMG, and restore [red]12 Signature Energy[/red]. \n - Becomes Invincible when casting [red]Phantom Annihilation[/red]. \n - If there are enough Dodge Gauge value, becomes Invincible when casting [red]Phantom Orbit[/red]. Otherwise, gains Super Armor and [red]50%[/red] DMG Reduction when casting [red]Phantom Orbit[/red].\n\n<strong>Dimensional Collapse: [blue]Dominator Form + Have the Collapse Mark + Press and Hold Dodge[/blue]</strong> \n Gathers energy and shatters the target's space. Pulls in nearby enemy units and deals Nihil DMG, gaining Signature Energy. [red]Collapse Points[/red] can amplify the damage. \n - [red]Collapse Points[/red] are capped at [red]360[/red]. Each [red]Collapse Point[/red] amplifies the Base DMG of [red]Dimensional Collapse[/red] by [red]0.5%[/red]. \n - Deals [red]3600%[/red] Nihil DMG. \n - Becomes Invincible and cannot cast [red]Signature - Silent Punishment[/red] during the process. \n - Gains [red]15 Signature Energy[/red] after casting.\n\n<strong>Agitated Beacon</strong>  \n When in the [red]Dominator Form[/red], Ishmael: Parhelion's Base DMG Efficiency dealt to Equilibrium Field increases by [red]100%[/red].",
