          "memory": "Build:Daemonissa",
          "bio": "The convergence of Las Prados's wealth and Project Winter's technologies coalesced into this frame. Its eerie quality emanates not merely from the Ascension-Network's favor but more profoundly from the ambitions and desires deep within her M.I.N.D., along with the secrets buried in history's obscured chapters.",
          "effect": "<strong>Body Trick</strong> \n Immediately gains 1 Red Orb after casting [red]Joker's Trickery[/red]. Max 1 Red Orb. Casting [red]Shadow's Guile[/red] after a Yellow Orb 3-Ping will enhance [red]Card Rank[/red] and grant Signature Energy.\n - Casting [red]Silk Threading / Blade Drawing / Shadow Breaking[/red] through a Yellow Orb 3-Ping will provide [red]20/20/30[/red] stackable Signature Energy for the next [red]Shadow's Guile[/red]. Max [red]70[/red] Signature Energy. Signature Energy will be cleared when Lilith exits [red]Crazy Gamble[/red]. \n - The first [red]Shadow's Guile[/red] cast after a Yellow Orb 3-Ping will enhance [red]Card Rank once[/red]. - Casting [red]Silk Threading / Blade Drawing / Shadow Breaking[/red] will grant [red]Red Orb - Shape Break / Red Orb - Soul Capture / Red Orb - Spiritual Judgement[/red] respectively. Max 1 Red Orb. When getting a duplicate, it will refresh the Red Orb type based on the previous Yellow Orb skill. If you already have [red]Red Orb - Spiritual Judgement[/red], it will not refresh before consumption.\n\n<strong>Hand Trick</strong> \n Ally units healed by Lilith: Daemonissa will be enhanced. Lilith heals herself upon casting [red]Invitation to a Radiant Dream[/red]. \n - Ally units healed by Lilith: Daemonissa will gain the [red]Dark Radiation[/red] effect which boosts their Dark DMG by [red]20%[/red] for [red]8s[/red]. Duration resets every time the effect is triggered. \n - If Lilith: Daemonissa has [red]Joker's Mark[/red], ally units will gain the [red]Lightning Surge[/red] effect instead, which boosts their Lightning DMG by [red]20%[/red] for [red]8s[/red]. Duration resets every time the effect is triggered. \n - Lilith restores HP equal to [red]40%[/red] of her ATK upon casting [red]Invitation to a Radiant Dream[/red].\n\n<strong>Shadow Trick</strong> \n When a character on team is in the Electric Storm Flash status, Lilith: Daemonissa will be regarded as she has the [red]Joker's Mark[/red].\n\n<strong>Card Trick</strong> \n Lilith: Daemonissa gains one Signal Orb upon triggering the Matrix. \n - If it is during [red]Crazy Gamble[/red], gains a Yellow Orb. If not, gains a Blue Orb instead.\n\n<strong>Effect: Plasma Beam</strong> \n Effect Charging: The Electric Charge is capped at 1000. \n - Effect Activated: Character with the Plasma Beam Effect enters the Electric Storm Flash status, launching lightning bolt strikes at nearby enemies every 2s and dealing [red]800%[/red] Plasma Beam DMG (without triggering Tank Class Skills) for 12s.",
