                  "description": "<strong>Lv. 1: [blue]Unlocked at S5 Rank[/blue]</strong>\nCasting [red]Night Embrace[/red], [red]Shadow's Guile[/red], or [red]Dreamfall Showdown[/red] will activate all available QTES.\n\n<strong>Lv. 2 — [blue]Unlocked at SS Rank[/blue]</strong> \n Each Signal Orb spent by [red]Joker's Trickery[/red] will increase the following [red]Shadow's Guile's[/red] Base DMG. The [red]1st to 3rd[/red] Signal Orbs pinged will each increase Base DMG by [red]20%[/red], while the [red]4th to 9th[/red] will each increase by [red]3%[/red]. All [red]9[/red] orbs will increase Base DMG by a total of [red]78%[/red] altogether. Casting [red]Shadow's Guile[/red] or [red]Dreamfall Showdown[/red] will clear the enhancement effect. [red]Each[/red] Yellow Orb spent during the [red]Night Embrace[/red] will increase the Base DMG of [red]Night Embrace - Return to Silence[/red] by [red]20%[/red] for this time.",
