          "memory": "Build:Pianissimo",
          "bio": "A specialized frame co-developed by the Science Council and the World Government Association of Art with improved stability of M.I.N.D. to deal with Transcendants. The adaptee can use it with a suppression device to perform combat skills of multiple parts playing simultaneously.",
          "effect": "<strong>Solo Realm</strong> \n Selena normally attacks [red]with her rapier[/red]. In the [red]Flow State[/red], she will attack [red]with the cello[/red] instead. She cannot enter the Matrix by dodging. It can only be triggered by [red]Basic Attack - Echoing Melody[/red]  / [red]Basic Attack - Inverted Divisi[/red]. Enters [red]Solo[/red] upon entering the Matrix triggered by herself.\n\n<strong>Concerto Orb: [blue]Flow State + Tap Concerto Orb[/blue]</strong> \n In the [red]Flow State[/red], 6 Signal Orbs will be converted to [red]Concerto Orbs[/red]. During the [red]Flow State[/red], Selena can only obtain and use [red]Concerto Orbs[/red]. After casting this skill, deals Physical DMG and gains [red]Musical Note(s)[/red], [red]Variation Point(s)[/red], [red]Melody Point(s)[/red], and [red]Signature Energy[/red]. Regains other Signal Orbs at the end of the [red]Flow State[/red]. \n - Deals [red]600%[/red] Physical DMG. \n - Gains 1 [red]Musical Note[/red] for each 3 [red]Concerto Orbs[/red] consumed. \n - When there are [red]Ice Spikes[/red], deals [red]1600%[/red] Glaciation DMG instead. \n - Gains [red]5 Variation Points[/red], [red]10 Melody Points[/red], and [red]5 Signature Energy[/red] after casting.\n\n<strong>Melodic Outburst: [blue]Flow State + 60 Melody Points + Press and Hold Dodge[/blue]</strong> \n In the [red]Flow State[/red], Selena can accumulate [red]Melody Points[/red] by casting [red]Concerto Orbs[/red], up to [red]60[/red]. Meanwhile, spends [red]60 Melody Points[/red] and summons a clone to attack, dealing Physical DMG and gaining [red]Variation Points[/red] and [red]Signature Energy[/red]. \n - Deals a total of [red]4000%[/red] Physical DMG. \n - When there are [red]Ice Spikes[/red], deals [red]10000%[/red] Glaciation DMG instead. \n - Becomes Invincible and cannot cast Signature in the process. Gains [red]30 Variation Points[/red] and [red]60 Signature Energy[/red] after casting.\n\n<strong>Grand Finale: [blue]Flow State + 100 Variation Points[/blue]</strong> \n In the [red]Flow State[/red], Selena can accumulate [red]Variation Points[/red] by casting specific skills, up to [red]100[/red]. At Max [red]Variation Points[/red], Selena will enter [red]Grand Finale[/red] and immediately gain [red]90 Signature Energy[/red]. \n - Removes all [red]Melody Points[/red] upon entering [red]Grand Finale[/red]. \n - [red]Grand Finale[/red] lasts [red]7s[/red]. After entering the [red]Grand Finale[/red], Selena will attack [red]with the rapier[/red] instead and will automatically cast [red]Signature - Majestic Interlude[/red] at the end. \n - During [red]Grand Finale[/red], Signal Orbs are infinite. \n - Clears all [red]Musical Notes[/red] at the end of [red]Grand Finale[/red].\n\n<strong>Effect: Glaciation</strong>\nSome of the skills can fill the [red]Glaciation Gauge[/red]. When the gauge is full, consume it to cast [red]Arctic Ice[/red], dealing Glaciation DMG and gaining [red]Arctic Ice Layers[/red]. Casting certain skills will consume all [red]Arctic Ice Layers[/red] to form [red]Ice Spikes[/red], dealing Glaciation DMG to nearby enemies. While [red]Ice Spikes[/red] persist, dealing Glaciation DMG will trigger [red]Ice Accumulation[/red], which deals additional Glaciation DMG and gains [red]Congelation[/red]. When [red]Ice Spikes[/red] expire, they will trigger [red]Ice Burst[/red] to deal Glaciation DMG based on the current [red]Congelation[/red].  The [red]Glaciation Gauge, Arctice Ice Layers, Ice Spikes[/red], and [red]Congelation[/red] can transfer to the next character with Effect: Glaciation.\n- At [red]100 Glaciation[/red], casts [red]Arctice Ice[/red] to deal [red]100%[/red] Glaciation DMG and generate [red]1 Arctic Ice Layer[/red]. Max [red]10 Layers[/red].\n- When having more than [red]0 Arctic Ice Layers[/red], certain skills can consume all [red]Arctic Ice Layers[/red] to form [red]Ice Spikes[/red], dealing [red]180%[/red] Glaciation DMG. When forming [red]Ice Spikes[/red], every [red]1 Arctic Ice Layer[/red] consumed will extend their duration by [red]1s[/red].\n- While [red]Ice Spikes[/red] persist, dealing Glaciation DMG will trigger [red]Ice Accumulation[/red], which deals [red]100%[/red] Glaciation DMG in a large area and gains [red]100 Congelation[/red]. This can only trigger [red]once[/red] every [red]0.25s[/red].\n- When [red]Ice Spikes[/red] expire, it will trigger [red]Ice Burst[/red] to deal [red]100%[/red] Glaciation DMG in a large area. For every [red]100 Congelation[/red] owned, the Base DMG of [red]Ice Burst[/red] increases by [red]9%[/red], up to [red]10000 Congelation[/red].",
          "priority": "Increases ATK by 10%. If Echoing Melody's Base DMG has been enhanced at the cost of Musical Notes, the next Rhythmic Piercing cast will enjoy the same amount of Base DMG Bonus. Casting Signature - Rainy Prelude will grant 3 Signal Orbs. Selena: Pianissimo gains up to 6 Signal Orbs every time upon entering the battlefield.",
