          "memory": "Build:Daybreak",
          "bio": "Say goodbye to the warm cradle and confront the painful awakening—she has traversed infinite loops to enter the real world with the full might of the matrix.",
          "effect": "<strong>Cluster Analysis</strong> \n Signal Orbs gained are converted into [red]Cluster Orbs[/red]. When not in the [red]Panoptic Segmentation[/red] Mode, Jetavie can only cast Yellow or Blue Orb Skills. After she enters [red]Panoptic Segmentation[/red], Red Orb Skills will be available. When entering [red]Charge Stance[/red] by pinging Signal Orbs, continuously restores Signature Energy, up to [red]40[/red]. Pinging [red]Cluster Orbs[/red] enhances the corresponding Charged Skill, up to [red]3[/red] times. When Extreme Dodge is triggered by pressing Dodge, gains [red]30[/red] Load Points instead of entering Matrix. When Dodge Gauge is empty, she can consume [red]10[/red] Load Points to perform a Dodge.\n\n<strong>Reflection Chain: [blue]During Kinetic Load enhanced by Cluster Orbs + Press and hold/Tap Basic Attack[/blue]</strong> \n Dashes toward the target and delivers a slashing attack, dealing Dark DMG while restoring [red]80[/red] Signature Energy. \n - Deals [red]1800%[/red] Dark DMG in total.\n\n<strong>Flaming Gush: [blue]During Kindled Blaze enhanced by Cluster Orbs + Press and hold/Tap Basic Attack[/blue]</strong> \n Leaps down from above to slash the target, converting Combustible into Ignition of equal stacks, dealing Ignition DMG and restoring [red]80[/red] Signature Energy. \n - Deals [red]2500%[/red] Ignition DMG in total. Jetavie gains [red]Coreflame Mark[/red] for [red]10[/red]s. Duration resets every time it is triggered.\n\n<strong>Forbidden Borders: [blue]Charge Stance + Release + Successful Dodge[/blue]</strong> \n While in Charge Stance, Jetavie can dodge attacks upon release. A successful dodge increases Extra DMG Bonus of the Charged Skill by [red]30%[/red]. During [red]Kinetic Load[/red] or [red]Kindled Blaze[/red], a successful dodge additionally returns [red]2[/red] Cluster Orbs.\n\n<strong>Sector Reconfiguration</strong> \n While in Charge Stance, consumes [red]250[/red] Dodge Gauge to block each incoming attack. If Dodge Gauge is insufficient, consumes [red]10 Load Points[/red] per block instead.\n\n<strong>Overflux Surge: [blue]During sword attacks + Tap Basic Attack repetitively[/blue]</strong> \n Wields the greatsword to continuously attack the target, dealing Dark DMG. \n - Basic Attack deals a total of [red]440%[/red] Dark DMG.\n\n<strong>Diffusive Function: [blue]During sword attacks + Dodge + Tap/Press and hold Basic Attack[/blue]</strong> \n During sword attacks, quickly transitions into casting [red]Crystalline Impact[/red] on the target, dealing Ignition DMG and applying Combustible Charges. \n - By tapping Dodge, deals [red]330%[/red] Ignition DMG and applies [red]1250[/red] Combustible Charges in total. \n - After pressing and holding Dodge, releases to deal [red]600%[/red] Ignition DMG and applies [red]1250[/red] Combustible Charges in total.\n\n<strong>Metamorphic Encoding: [blue]During sword attacks + Press and hold Basic Attack to charge[/blue]</strong> \n During sword attacks, quickly transitions into casting [red]Kinetic Load / Kindled Blaze[/red] on the target, dealing damage. [red]Kinetic Load / Kindled Blaze[/red] cast this way cannot be followed up with other attacks. \n - Charges partially to cast [red]Kindled Blaze[/red], dealing [red]250%[/red] Ignition DMG in total. \n - Charges fully to cast [red]Kinetic Load[/red], dealing [red]250%[/red] Dark DMG in total.\n\n<strong>Effect: Ignition</strong>\nCombustible: Every [red]250[/red] Combustible Charges will add [red]1[/red] Combustible stack, up to 20 stacks.\nIgnition: Ignited units take Ignition DMG equal to [red]Ignition stacks x30%[/red] (Tank Skills will not be triggered) every second for 10s.\n- The subsequent unit will inherit the Combustible/Ignition status of the last unit on the battlefield upon its death.",
          "priority": "ATK increases by 10%. Returns 1 Cluster Orb for every 3 Cluster Orbs consumed. Extra DMG Bonus of Reflection Chain and Flaming Gush increases by 20%.",
