          "cub": {
              "name": "wrathfang",
              "notes": "Wrathfang will attack the target with a blade of light in the mouth, pulling in nearby enemies and dealing DMG."
          },
          "memory": "Build:Geiravor",
          "bio": "A test frame developed by Kurono. It failed the berserk test after activation and was abandoned during a mission. Years later, Vera reactivated the frame, seized its control after fierce combats and chaos, and named it \"Geiravor\".",
          "effect": "<strong>Schism Strike</strong> \n During [red]Untamed Impulse[/red], Vera: Geiravor can cast only Blue Orbs, and her Basic Attacks generate only Blue Orbs. \n - After entering [red]Last Blaze[/red], she can cast only Red Orbs, and her Basic Attacks generate only Red Orbs. \n - Upon entering [red]Last Blaze[/red], retains any unused Blue Orbs from [red]Untamed Impulse[/red]. \n - Upon exiting [red]Last Blaze[/red], converts all existing Red Orbs into Blue Orbs. \n - When exiting the battlefield during [red]Last Blaze[/red], clears all existing Blue and Red Orbs, then gains [red]2[/red] Blue Orbs upon re-entry. \n - Each cast of [red]QTE - Infernal Silhouette[/red] additionally increases her Base DMG by [red]25%[/red] the next time she enters [red]Absolute Pyre[/red], up to [red]50%[/red]. \n\n<strong>Shadowhunt Tremor: [blue]During Untamed Impulse + Press and Hold Basic Attack[/blue]</strong> \n Vera: Geiravor strikes the enemy with her lance, dealing Fire DMG. Gains Super Armor while casting this skill. \n - When casting a partially charged [red]Shadowhunt Tremor[/red], deals [red]400%[/red] Fire DMG, gains [red]12[/red] Signature Energy, and restores [red]50%[/red] of max HP. \n - When casting a fully charged [red]Shadowhunt Tremor[/red], deals [red]1000%[/red] Fire DMG, gains [red]24[/red] Signature Energy, and restores [red]100%[/red] of max HP.\n\n<strong>Hellfire Crucible: [blue]During Last Blaze + 20 Rekindled Doom + Press and Hold Basic Attack[/blue]</strong> \n Vera: Geiravor wields her lance to attack, dealing [red]1000%[/red] Fire DMG and entering the [red]Hellfire Crucible Combo[/red]. Gains [red]10[/red] Signature Energy and Super Armor in the process. Casting this skill consumes [red]20 Rekindled Doom[/red]. \n - Based on the number of Yellow Orbs cleared by [red]Tempered in Midnight[/red], converts [red]Final Embers[/red] into HP. \n - When [red]1 / 2 / 3 / 4[/red] Yellow Orbs are cleared by [red]Tempered in Midnight[/red], converts [red]10% / 15% / 20% / 25%[/red] of the current [red]Final Embers[/red] into her HP. \n - When [red]5 / 6[/red] Yellow Orbs are cleared by [red]Tempered in Midnight[/red], converts [red]Final Embers[/red] equal to [red]10% / 15%[/red] of her max HP into her HP. \n - If [red]Penal Immersion[/red] is active, Vera: Geiravor instead deals [red]300%[/red] Darkflow DMG and gains [red]200[/red] Darkflow Reserve.\n\n<strong>Razor Whirlwind: [blue]During Last Blaze + After Hellfire Crucible Combo + 20 Rekindled Doom + Press and Hold Basic Attack[/blue]</strong> \n Flames erupt from the tip of Vera: Geiravor's lance as she exits the [red]Hellfire Crucible Combo[/red], dealing [red]1600%[/red] Fire DMG and entering the [red]Razor Whirlwind Combo[/red]. Gains [red]20[/red] Signature Energy and Super Armor in the process. Casting this skill consumes [red]20 Rekindled Doom[/red]. \n - Based on the number of Yellow Orbs cleared by [red]Tempered in Midnight[/red], converts [red]Final Embers[/red] into HP. \n - When [red]1 / 2 / 3 / 4[/red] Yellow Orbs are cleared by [red]Tempered in Midnight[/red], converts [red]20% / 30% / 40% / 50%[/red] of the current [red]Final Embers[/red] into her HP. \n - When [red]5 / 6[/red] Yellow Orbs are cleared by [red]Tempered in Midnight[/red], converts [red]Final Embers[/red] equal to [red]15% / 20%[/red] of her max HP into her HP. \n - If [red]Penal Immersion[/red] is active, Vera: Geiravor instead deals [red]500%[/red] Darkflow DMG and gains [red]400[/red] Darkflow Reserve.\n\n<strong>Rending Ravage: [blue]During Last Blaze + After Razor Whirlwind Combo + 20 Rekindled Doom + Press and Hold Basic Attack[/blue]</strong> \n Vera: Geiravor swings her lance with relentless battle resolve, dealing [red]3200%[/red] Fire DMG and exiting the [red]Razor Whirlwind Combo[/red]. Gains [red]70[/red] Signature Energy and Super Armor in the process. Casting this skill consumes [red]20 Rekindled Doom[/red]. \n - Based on the number of Yellow Orbs cleared by [red]Tempered in Midnight[/red], converts [red]Final Embers[/red] into HP. \n - When [red]1 / 2 / 3 / 4[/red] Yellow Orbs are cleared by [red]Tempered in Midnight[/red], converts [red]30% / 50% / 70% / 90%[/red] of the current [red]Final Embers[/red] into her HP. \n - When [red]5 / 6[/red] Yellow Orbs are cleared by [red]Tempered in Midnight[/red], converts [red]Final Embers[/red] equal to [red]50% / 55%[/red] of her max HP into her HP. \n - If [red]Penal Immersion[/red] is active, Vera: Geiravor instead deals [red]700%[/red] Darkflow DMG and gains [red]1000[/red] Darkflow Reserve.\n\n'''Dawnbreaker's Rush<strong> \n When Vera: Geiravor takes damage during [red]Last Blaze[/red], converts [red]20%[/red] of HP lost into [red]Final Embers[/red]. \n - The value of [red]Final Embers[/red] gained cannot exceed her max HP. \n - Gains DMG Reduction based on the current [red]Final Embers[/red]. \n - When the current value of [red]Final Embers[/red] is below [red]50%[/red] of max HP, gains [red]20%[/red] DMG Reduction. \n - When the current value of [red]Final Embers[/red] is below [red]|75%[/red] but no less than [red]50%[/red] of max HP, gains [red]50%[/red] DMG Reduction. \n - When the current value of [red]Final Embers[/red] is no less than [red]75%[/red] of max HP, gains [red]75%[/red] DMG Reduction. \n - After being generated, [red]Final Embers last for 5s[/red] before starting to decrease. This countdown resets when [red]Final Embers[/red] are converted into HP or new [red]Final Embers[/red] are generated. \n - Converts all [red]Final Embers[/red] into HP at the end of battle.\n\n</strong>Nocturne Incineration<strong> \n Allies healed by Vera: Geiravor gain the [red]Fire Tempered[/red] effect that increases Fire DMG by [red]20%[/red] for [red]8s[/red]. Duration resets every time it is triggered. \n - If there is [red]at least 1 Darkflow stack[/red], allies healed by her instead gain the [red]Dark Radiation[/red] effect that increases Dark DMG by [red]20%[/red] for [red]8s[/red]. Duration resets every time it is triggered. \n - Converting [red]Final Embers[/red] into HP does not count as healing.\n\n</strong>Effect: Darkflow''' \n Every [red]200[/red] Darkflow Reserve grants 1 Darkflow stack, up to a maximum of 15. Characters with the Darkflow Effect will gain a Darkflow Aura based on the current Darkflow stacks, dealing a small amount of Darkflow DMG over time to enemies and reducing their HP recovery. When the Darkflow stacks reach the threshold, the Aura upgrades, increasing its area of effect and dealing massive Darkflow DMG to enemies within the area. \n - [red]1 / 3 / 6 / 10 / 15[/red] stacks: Deals [red]100% / 200% / 400% / 800% / 1600%[/red] Darkflow DMG, then deals [red]20% / 40% / 60% / 80% / 100%[/red] Darkflow DMG per second, reducing enemy HP recovery by [red]10% / 20% / 30% / 50% / 100%[/red].",
