          "memory": "Build:Dante",
          "bio": "The boss of Devil May Cry, and the most powerful devil hunter alive. Revered for his legendary strength.",
          "effect": "<strong>Devil Arm Energy</strong>\nWhen pinging Signal Orbs via [red]Devil Sword Dante[/red], [red]Dr. Fause[/red], or [red]Balrog[/red], or when casting [red]DSD Combo[/red] or [red]Balrog Combo[/red], gains [red]Devil Arm Energy[/red]. When [red]Devil Arm Energy[/red] is full, spends [red]Devil Arm Energy[/red] to enhance the effects of [red]Dance Macabre[/red], [red]Real Impact[/red], and [red]Red Hot Night[/red].\n- A complete [red]DSD Combo / Balrog Combo[/red] grants [red]4 / 1[/red] points of [red]Devil Arm Energy[/red] respectively.\n- When casting [red]Devil Sword Dante / Dr. Faust - Set Hat / Balrog[/red] gains [red]1 / 2 / 6[/red] points of [red]Devil Arm Energy[/red] based on the number of orbs pinged. For every Signal Orb pinged during [red]Dr. Faust: Red Hot Night - Charge[/red], gains [red]1 Devil Arm Energy[/red].\n- When casting [red]Dance Macabre[/red] with full [red]DT[/red], if [red]Devil Arm Energy[/red] is full, spends all of it and gains [red]40[/red] Signature Energy, [red]400 Judgement Points[/red], and a [red]Devilsword Mark[/red].\n- When casting [red]Real Impact[/red] with full [red]DT[/red], if [red]Devil Arm Energy[/red] is full, spends all of it and gains [red]40[/red] Signature Energy, [red]400 Judgement Points[/red], and an [red]Ignition Mark[/red]\n- When casting [red]Dr. Faust: Red Hot Night - Burst[/red], if [red]DT[/red] is full, spends all [red]Devil Arm Energy[/red] and gains [red]25 Judgement Points[/red] for [red]every[/red] Devil Arm Energy spent, and the Base DMG of this cast of [red]Dr. Faust: Red Hot Night - Burst[/red] cast and the next cast of [red]Sin Devil Trigger[/red] increases by [red]12.5%[/red], up to [red]150%[/red]. When cast at maximum charge, gains an additional [red]28[/red] Signature Energy.\n- Up to [red]12 Devil Arm Energy[/red] can be possessed at a time.\n\n<strong>Devil Arms Mastery</strong>\nGain [red]3[/red] Signal Orbs upon entering battle. Dante gains different enhancements when he possesses different Marks.\n- [red]Devilsword Mark[/red]: Base DMG of [red]Dance Macabre[/red] at full [red]DT[/red], [red]SDT - Sin Stinger[/red], [red]SDT - The Luce[/red], and [red]SDT - Demolition[/red] increases by [red]100%[/red].\n- [red]Ignition Mark[/red]: For every stack of [red]Ignition[/red] on the enemy, Base DMG of [red]Real Impact[/red] at full [red]DT[/red], [red]SDT - Sin Stinger[/red], [red]SDT - The Luce[/red], and [red]SDT - Demolition[/red] increases by [red]5%[/red]. When dealing DMG to enemies with [red]Ignition[/red], extends the duration of [red]Ignition[/red] by [red]0.9s[/red]. TTriggers up to once per enemy, with trigger count resetting when the enemy is inflicted with [red]Ignition[/red] once again.\n- Dante can only possess one Mark at a time.\n\n<strong>SDT</strong>\nSpends [red]SDT[/red], dealing DMG and gaining [red]Judgement Points[/red]. Upon cast, triggers Matrix if it is not on cooldown.\n- Press and hold Red/Blue Orbs to cast [red]SDT[/red] skills. Every [red]30[/red] points of [red]SDT[/red] spent grants [red]38[/red] Signature Energy and [red]100 Judgement Points[/red].\n- Press and hold Red Orbs to cast [red]SDT - Sin Stinger[/red], gathering nearby targets and dealing [red]630%[/red] Fire DMG. If Dante possesses an [red]Ignition Mark[/red] upon casting, deals [red]910%[/red] Ignition DMG and gains [red]1000[/red] points of Combustible Charge instead. Gains [red]80%[/red] DMG Reduction while casting.\n- Press and hold Blue Orbs to cast [red]SDT - The Luce[/red], dealing [red]630%[/red] Fire DMG. If Dante possess an [red]Ignition Mark[/red] upon casting, deals [red]910%[/red] Ignition DMG and gains [red]1000[/red] points of Combustible Charge instead. Gains [red]80%[/red] DMG Reduction while casting.\n- When there are [red]120[/red] points of [red]DT[/red], tap Yellow Orbs to spend all [red]DT[/red] to cast [red]SDT - Demolition[/red], gaining [red]152[/red] Signature Energy and [red]400 Judgement Points[/red]. [red]SDT - Demolition[/red] gathers targets in a large area and deals [red]2300%[/red] Fire DMG. If Dante possesses an [red]Ignition Mark[/red] upon casting, deals [red]3100%[/red] Ignition DMG and gains [red]4000[/red] points of Combustible Charge instead. Gains [red]80%[/red] DMG Reduction while casting.\n- [red]SDT[/red] is capped at [red]120[/red] points.\n\n<strong>Royal Guard – [blue]Do Not Move Joystick + Dodge[/blue]</strong>\nBlock an enemy's attack. Pressing and holding Dodge continuously depletes Dodge Gauge. Release the block to deal Fire DMG in retaliation.\n- Deals [red]90%[/red] Fire DMG. If released right when an enemy is attacking, triggers a Royal Release instead, dealing [red]120%[/red] Fire DMG.\n- While pressing and holding Dodge, consumes [red]60[/red] Dodge Gauge every second.\n\n<strong>Trickster – [blue]Move Joystick + Press and Hold Dodge[/blue]</strong>\nWhen cast on the ground, blinks above the enemy.\n\n<strong>High Time – [blue]Human Form + Tap Jump[/blue]</strong>\nJumps upward. When cast midair, press and hold to blink to the ground below the enemy.\n- If held when casting on the ground, launches an enemy into the air instead, dealing [red]150%[/red] Fire DMG.\n- When in midair, Dodge Gauge refills [red]300%[/red] faster.\n\n<strong>Fire Weapons – [blue]Tap Firearm button[/blue]</strong>\nShoots the enemy, dealing Fire DMG.\n- If cast on the ground in [red]Human Form[/red] while using Devil Sword Dante, deals [red]120%[/red] Fire DMG. If cast while using Balrog, deals [red]180%[/red] Fire DMG. If pushing the joystick upon casting, deals [red]200%[/red] Fire DMG instead.\n- If cast midair in in [red]Human Form[/red] while using Devil Sword Dante, deals [red]120%[/red] Fire DMG. If pushing the joystick upon casting, deals [red]260%[/red] Fire DMG instead. If cast while using Balrog, deals [red]180%[/red] Fire DMG.\n- If [red]SDT Form[/red] is active while casting, deals [red]120%[/red] Fire DMG.\n\n<strong>Provocation – [blue]Human Form + Aerial + Press and Hold Core Passive Bar[/blue]</strong>\nThrows a rose at the enemy.\n\n<strong>Conjured Swords</strong>\nSummons [red]Conjured Swords[/red] to deal [red]1%[/red] Fire DMG.\n- When in [red]Human Form[/red], tapping Core Passive Bar summons [red]Conjured Swords[/red] that launch the enemy into the air. If pushing the joystick upon casting, [red]Conjured Swords[/red] thrust at the enemy instead.\n\n<strong>Effect: Ignition</strong>\nCombustible: Every [red]250[/red] Combustible Charges will add [red]1[/red] Combustible stack, up to 20 stacks.\n- Ignition: Ignited units take Ignition DMG equal to [red]Ignition stacks x30%[/red]  every second (Tank Skills will not be triggered) for 10s.\n- The subsequent unit will inherit the Combustible/Ignition status of the last unit on the battlefield upon its death.",
          "priority": "ATK increases by 10%. After casting SDT - Sin Inferno or SDT - Final Judgement, gains a Signal Orb and converts the remaining SDT into DT. For every 30 SDT converted, additionally gains a Signal Orb. When more than 60 SDT is converted, gains 6 Devil Arm Energy.",
