                  "description": "<strong>Lv. 1 — [blue]Unlocked at SS3 Rank[/blue]</strong>\nAfter casting [red]SDT - Sin Inferno[/red] or [red]SDT - Final Judgement[/red], Base DMG of QTE throughout the battle increases by [red]1000%[/red]. Base DMG of [red]Devil Sword Dante[/red], [red]Dr. Faust[/red], and [red]Balrog[/red] increases by [red]100%[/red]. Base DMG of [red]Dance Macabre[/red] and [red]Real Impact[/red] cast at full [red]DT[/red] increases by [red]100%[/red].\n\n<strong>Lv. 2 — [blue]Unlocked at SSS Rank[/blue]</strong>\nDuring [red]Departed State[/red], Dante’s Extra DMG Bonus increases by [red]100%[/red]. Base DMG of [red]SDT - Sin Inferno[/red] and [red]SDT - Final Judgement[/red] increases by [red]1.7[/red] times. If Dante possess an [red]Ignition Mark[/red] when casting the aforementioned skills, their Base DMG increases by [red]2.1[/red] times instead.",
