                  "description": "<strong>Lv. 1 – [blue]Unlocked at SSS3 Rank[/blue]</strong>\nExtra DMG Bonus of [red]Devil Sword Dante[/red], [red]Dr. Faust[/red], and [red]Balrog[/red], as well as [red]Dance Macabre[/red] and [red]Real Impact[/red] cast at full [red]DT[/red] increases by [red]70%[/red].\n\n<strong>Lv. 2 — [blue]Unlocked at SSS6 Rank[/blue]</strong>\nExtra DMG Bonus of [red]SDT - Sin Stinger[/red], [red]SDT - The Luce[/red], and [red]SDT - Demolition[/red] increases by [red]60%[/red].\n\n<strong>Lv. 3 — [blue]Unlocked at SSS+ Rank[/blue]</strong>\nExtra DMG Bonus of [red]Sin Devil Trigger[/red] increases by [red]40%[/red].",
