              {
                  "name": "Yellow Orb: Beowulf",
                  "description": "<strong>Kick 13 – [blue]Wielding Beowulf + Tap Yellow Orb[/blue]</strong>\n Vergil kicks and deals [red]400% / 800% / 1200%[/red] Physical DMG (deals [red]600% / 1200% / 1800%[/red] Physical DMG when in SDT form). Recovers a total of [red]50 / 100 / 150 points of SDT[/red] over time. Gains Super Armor during 3-Pings.\n - During end lag, press and hold Basic Attack to make Vergil cast Rising Sun (regarded as a Basic Attack), dealing [red]1600%[/red] Physical DMG ([red]2400%[/red] Physical DMG when in SDT Form) and restoring [red]150 points of SDT[/red]. Vergil gains Super Armor meanwhile.\n - Casting Rising Sun will make the next Judgment Cut End deal Physical DMG instead.\n - When cast with no Devil Soul owned, Vergil cannot gain [red]Signature Energy / SDT[/red].\n\n<strong>Weapon Switching – [blue]Without Beowulf + Tap Yellow Orb[/blue]</strong>\n Vergil switches his weapon to Beowulf.",
                  "icon": "YEL"
              },
              {
                  "name": "Blue Orb: Mirage Edge",
                  "description": "<strong>Drive – [blue]Wielding Mirage Edge + Tap Blue Orb[/blue]</strong>\n Vergil launches a reverse grip slash, dealing [red]240% / 480% / 720%[/red] Ultima Slash DMG ([red]340% / 680% / 1020%[/red] Ultima Slash DMG when in SDT Form) and restoring a total of [red]50 / 100 / 150 points of SDT[/red]. Gains Super Armor during 3-Pings.\n - During end lag, press and hold Basic Attack to charge and cast Over Drive (regarded as a Basic Attack), restoring [red]150 points of SDT[/red], dealing [red]480% / 640% / 800% / 1280%[/red] Ultima Slash DMG ([red]720% / 960% / 1200% / 1920%[/red] Ultima Slash DMG when in SDT Form) based on Charge Level 0-3 and accumulating [red]100 / 300 / 400 / 600 Sharp Reserve[/red] for the team. Vergil gains Super Armor meanwhile.\n - When cast with no Devil Soul owned, Vergil cannot gain [red]Signature Energy / SDT[/red].\n\n<strong>Weapon Switching – [blue]Without Mirage Edge + Tap Blue Orb[/blue]</strong> \n Vergil switches his weapon to Mirage Edge.",
                  "icon": "BLU"
              },
              {
                  "name": "Basic Attack: Trigger Heart",
                  "description": "<strong>Yamato Combo — [blue]With Yamato + Tap Basic Attack[/blue]</strong>\n Launches 3 attacks with Yamato, dealing a total of [red]300%[/red] Ultima Slash DMG (or a total of [red]420%[/red] Ultima Slash DMG when in SDT Form). Keep tapping Basic Attack afterward to follow up with a vertical slash, dealing [red]160%[/red] Ultima Slash DMG ([red]240%[/red] Ultima Slash DMG when in SDT Form). Keep tapping Basic Attack afterward in SDT Form to follow up with a triple slash, dealing [red]520%[/red] Ultima Slash DMG. If SDT Form ends during the process, then deals [red]400%[/red] Ultima Slash DMG instead.\n - If Vergil is in SDT Form, each of the abovementioned Basic Attack will consume 1 Devil Soul (and restore 2 Devil Souls in Matrix status), increase Base DMG by [red]100%[/red], and restore [red]14 Signature Energy and 30 JCE Points[/red]. Shortly pause after the 3 attacks and tap Basic Attack to follow up with a chain slash, dealing [red]200%[/red] Ultima Slash DMG ([red]300%[/red] Ultima Slash DMG when in SDT Form). Tap basic Attack afterward to follow up with a horizontal slash, dealing [red]260%[/red] Ultima Slash DMG ([red]400%[/red] Ultima Slash DMG when in SDT Form).\n\n<strong>Beowulf Combo – [blue]With Beowulf + Tap Basic Attack[/blue]</strong>\n Launches 4 attacks with Beowulf, or 5 attacks if in SDT Form. Vergil can charge during each of these attacks and deal [red]100% / 160% / 320% / 480%[/red] Physical DMG ([red]160% / 240% / 480% / 720%[/red] Physical DMG when in SDT Form) based on Charge Level 0-3.\n - If Vergil is in SDT Form, each of these attacks will restore [red]9 Signature Energy and 5 / 10 / 20 / 30 JCE Points (based on Charge Level).[/red]\n\n<strong>Mirage Edge Combo – [blue]With Mirage Edge + Tap Basic Attack[/blue]</strong>\n Launches a two-hit combo with Mirage Edge, dealing a total of [red]320%[/red] Ultima Slash DMG (or a total of [red]480%[/red] Ultima Slash DMG when in SDT Form. Each hit restores [red]30 JCE Points[/red].) Keep tapping Basic Attack afterward to follow up with a thrust, dealing [red]320%[/red] Ultima Slash DMG ([red]480%[/red] Ultima Slash DMG when in SDT Form).\n\n<strong>Million Stab – [blue]Mirage Edge equipped + Move Joystick + Dodge + Press and hold Basic Attack OR During the end lag of a two-hit combo + Quickly tap Basic Attack[/blue]</strong>\n Casts up to 2 chain stabs, with each stab dealing [red]400%[/red] Ultima Slash DMG. Automatically follows-up with a finishing stab afterward, dealing [red]800%[/red] Ultima Slash DMG. If Vergil is in SDT Form, each chain stab will deal [red]600%[/red] Ultima Slash DMG and trigger an Ultima Slash. Meanwhile, each chain stab can consume 1 Devil Soul (and restore 2 Devil Souls in Matrix status), increase Base DMG by [red]100%[/red], and restore [red]11 Signature Energy and 15 JCE Points[/red]. If Vergil is in SDT Form, keep pressing or quickly tapping Basic Attack after the 2 chain stabs to increase the number of chain stabs. Vergil will deal [red]1200%[/red] Ultima Slash DMG and restore [red]11 Signature Energy[/red] through the finishing stab in SDT Form.\n\n<strong>Aerial Strike – [blue]Midair + Tap Basic Attack[/blue]</strong>\n Vergil launches an aerial attack. [red]Yamato - Aerial Rave[/red] deals [red]560%[/red] Ultima Slash DMG ([red]820%[/red] Ultima Slash DMG when in SDT Form). [red]Beowulf - Aerial Lunar Phase[/red] deals [red]200%[/red] Physical DMG ([red]300%[/red] Physical DMG when in SDT Form). [red]Mirage Edge - Helm Breaker Slash[/red] deals [red]200%[/red] Ultima Slash DMG ([red]300%[/red] Ultima Slash DMG when in SDT Form).\n\n<strong>Dodge Combo – [blue]Dodge + Tap Basic Attack[/blue]</strong> \n Vergil dodges and then attacks. [red]Yamato - Rapid Slash[/red] deals [red]120%[/red] Ultima Slash DMG ([red]160%[/red] Ultima Slash DMG when in SDT Form). [red]Beowulf - Lunar Phase[/red] deals [red]160%[/red] Physical DMG ([red]240%[/red] Physical DMG when in SDT Form). [red]Mirage Edge - Stinger[/red] deals [red]260%[/red] Ultima Slash DMG ([red]400%[/red] Ultima Slash DMG when in SDT Form). Recovers 250 Dodge Gauge within 2.5s after casting.\n\n<strong>Jump – [blue]Tap Jump[/blue]</strong>\n Vergil jumps. Deals [red]60%[/red] Physical DMG when carrying Beowulf.\n\n<strong>Upper Slash – [blue]With Yamato/Mirage Edge + Ground + Press and Hold Jump[/blue]</strong>\n Vergil casts an upper slash. If carrying Yamato, deals [red]200%[/red] Ultima Slash DMG ([red]300%[/red] Ultima Slash DMG when in SDT Form). If carrying Mirage Edge, dealing [red]160%[/red] Ultima Slash DMG ([red]240%[/red] Ultima Slash DMG when in SDT Form).\n\n<strong>Beowulf - Uppercut – [blue]With Beowulf + Press and Hold Jump[/blue]</strong>\n Casts a Rising Attack with Beowulf. Launches Beast Uppercut / Rising Dragon / Dragon Breaker / Enhanced Dragon Breaker respectively based on Charge Level 0-3, dealing [red]80% / 100% / 240% / 340%[/red] Physical DMG ([red]100% / 160% / 340% / 480%[/red] Physical DMG when in SDT Form). When casting Dragon Breaker / Enhanced Dragon Breaker in SDT Form, casts Dragon Breaker 2 / Enhanced Dragon Breaker 2 instead, dealing [red]580% / 880%[/red] Physical DMG, which cannot be interrupted. If SDT Form ends during the process, then deals [red]400% / 580%[/red] Physical DMG instead.\n - Casting Dragon Breaker 2 / Enhanced Dragon Breaker 2 in SDT Form will restore [red]24 Signature Energy and 40 / 80 JCE Points[/red] and consume up to 7 Devil Souls (and restore 3 Devil Souls in Matrix), with each Devil Soul consumed increasing Base DMG by [red]100%[/red] and restoring [red]6 Signature Energy and 10 JCE Points[/red].\n\n<strong>Plunge Strike – [blue]Midair + Tap Jump[/blue]</strong>\n Vergil casts a plunge attack. [red]Yamato - Aerial Cleave[/red] deals [red]200%[/red] Ultima Slash DMG ([red]320%[/red] Ultima Slash DMG when in SDT Form). [red]Beowulf - Starfall[/red] deals [red]160%[/red] Physical DMG ([red]200%[/red] Physical DMG when in SDT Form). [red]Mirage Edge - Helm Breaker Cleave[/red] deals [red]160%[/red] Ultima Slash DMG ([red]200%[/red] Ultima Slash DMG when in SDT Form).",
                  "icon": "BAS"
              },
              {
                  "name": "Signature: Sin Devil Trigger",
                  "description": "<strong>Sin Devil Trigger – [blue]Not in SDT Form + 300 Points of SDT + Tap Signature[/blue]</strong>\n Vergil unleashes the power of the devil blood and enters SDT Form, causing a DT Burst, dealing [red]1080%[/red] Ultima Slash DMG, and triggering [red]Time Lag Calculation[/red].\n In SDT Form, Vergil will have greatly enhanced strength, speed, special abilities, [red]gain Super Armor, and deal more damage through all skills[/red]. However, he will not be able to restore Devil Souls or Signature Energy through Basic Attacks or pinging orbs in SDT Form.\n - In SDT Form, Vergil consumes [red]20 points of SDT[/red] every second and cannot restore SDT. He will automatically exit SDT Form at 0 SDT.\n - Casting this skill will not interrupt any Basic Attack.\n\n<strong>Judgment Cut End – [blue]90 Signature Energy + Not in SDT Form, Press and hold Signature / In SDT Form, tap Signature[/blue]</strong> \n Vergil casts his Ultimate Ability, shattering space and time, clearing all SDT, and dealing [red]1280%[/red] Ultima Slash DMG ([red]1920%[/red] Ultima Slash DMG when in SDT Form). Triggers [red]Time Lag Calculation[/red]  meanwhile.\n - Each JCE Point will increase Judgment Cut End's Base DMG by [red]0.6%[/red], up to [red]300[/red] Points.\n - Judgment Cut End will always consume the remaining Truewill and deal bonus [red]360%[/red] Ultima Slash DMG per Truewill consumed.",
                  "icon": "SIG"
              },
              {
                  "name": "QTE: Judgment Cut Fall",
                  "description": "<strong>[blue]Tap QTE[/blue]</strong>\n Vergil casts Judgment Cut, dealing [red]600%[/red] Physical DMG.",
                  "icon": "QTE"
              },
              {
                  "name": "Core Passive: Devil Hunter Skill",
                  "description": "<strong>Judgment Cut – [blue]With Yamato + Press and Hold Red Orb/Basic Attack/Jump + Release Button[/blue]</strong>\n Casts Judgment Cut after performing the corresponding action, dealing [red]960%[/red] Ultima Slash DMG.\n When Vergil is in SDT Form, Judgment Cut has a bigger range and deals [red]1440%[/red] Ultima Slash DMG. Meanwhile, he can spend up to 3 Devil Souls and restore [red]7 Signature Energy and 5 JCE Points[/red] per Devil Soul consumed.\n - When team has more than 3 Truewill and Vergil is in SDT Form, Judgment Cut will consume [red]3 Truewill[/red], have [red]30%[/red] higher Base DMG, deal fixed [red]600%[/red] Ultima Slash DMG, and restore [red]25 JCE Points[/red].\n - Release the corresponding button when the weapon glows to cast Precise Judgment Cut, up to 3 times. If Vergil is in SDT Form, keep holding Basic Attack to cast Judgment Cut continuously, and consuming Devil Souls is regarded as Precise Judgment Cut. Precise Judgment Cuts can be cast at a faster speed.\n\n<strong>Round Trip – [blue]With Mirage Edge + Press and Hold Blue Orb/Basic Attack/Jump Until Weapon Glows + Release Button[/blue]</strong>\n Throws out Mirage Edge after the corresponding action, dealing [red]520%[/red] Ultima Slash DMG ([red]780%[/red] Ultima Slash DMG when in SDT Form).\n - Casting a Mirage Edge skill after throwing the blade out will call it back in priority.\n\n<strong>Doppelganger</strong>\n In SDT Form, Vergil will launch joint attacks with his Doppelganger. Each joint attack deals [red]160%[/red] Ultima Slash DMG.\n\n<strong>Air Trick – [blue]Ground + Locked-on Enemy + Not Push Joystick + Press and Hold Dodge[/blue]</strong>\n Vergil quickly approaches the locked-on enemy.\n\n<strong>Provocation – [blue]Tap Core Passive Bar[/blue]</strong> \n Vergil taunts the enemy, dealing [red]1%[/red] Ultima Slash DMG.\n\n<strong>Mirage Blades – [blue]Netherworld Arm Not Charged + Tap Netherworld Arm[/blue]</strong>\n Deals [red]2%[/red] Ultima Slash DMG with Mirage Blades.\n - This skill can be cast without any Netherworld Arm equipped.\n\n<strong>Blistering / Heavy Rain Blades – [blue]Netherworld Arm Charged + Push/Not Push Joystick + Tap Netherworld Arm[/blue]</strong>\n Blistering: Deals [red]200%[/red] Ultima Slash DMG ([red]320%[/red] Ultima Slash DMG when carrying Netherworld Arm - Mirage Blades).\n Heavy Rain: Deals [red]200%[/red] Ultima Slash DMG and slows enemy unit down. Deals [red]320%[/red] Ultima Slash DMG when carrying Netherworld Arm - Mirage Blades.\n - Equipping a Netherworld Arm other than mirage Blades will trigger the corresponding active skill.\n\n<strong>Storm / Spiral Blades – [blue]Netherworld Arm Charged + Push/Not Push Joystick + Press and Hold Netherworld Arm[/blue]</strong> \n Storm: Deals [red]200%[/red] Ultima Slash DMG. Deals [red]320%[/red] Ultima Slash DMG when carrying Netherworld Arm - Mirage Blades.\n Spiral: Deals [red]200%[/red] Ultima Slash DMG. Deals [red]320%[/red] Ultima Slash DMG when carrying Netherworld Arm - Mirage Blades.\n - Equipping a Netherworld Arm that is not Mirage Blades will trigger the Netherworld Arm's Active Skill.\n\n<strong>Effect: Ultima Slash</strong> \n Certain skills build up [red]Sharp Reserve[/red]. [red]Sharp Reserve[/red] can be passed on to the next character affected by Ultima Slash effect, up to [red]999[/red] points.\n - When [red]Sharp Reserve[/red] reaches [red]100[/red] points, the next skill with [red]Ultima Slash[/red] effect that hits an enemy will consume [red]100 points of Sharp Reserve[/red] to trigger a [red]Ultima Slash[/red], dealing [red]400%[/red] Ultima Slash DMG.\n - Gains [red]1[/red] point of [red]Truewill[/red] each time it triggers, up to [red]90[/red] points.",
                  "icon": "COR"
              },
              {
                  "name": "Leader: The Alpha and the Omega",
                  "description": "All team members deal [red]10%[/red] more Physical DMG and Ultima Slash DMG. Attackers gain [red]10%[/red] ATK.",
                  "icon": "LEA"
              },
              {
                  "name": "SS Rank: Bury the Light within the Blade",
                  "description": "<strong>Lv. 1: [blue]Unlocked at S5 Rank[/blue]</strong>\n Casting [red]Sin Devil Trigger[/red] and [red]Judgment Cut End[/red] will activate all available QTEs.\n\n<strong>Lv. 2: [blue]Unlocked at SS Rank[/blue]</strong>\n Restores 3 Devil Souls when switched in.\n Vergil gains [red]20%[/red] CRIT DMG when in SDT Form.\n After casting [red]Judgment Cut End[/red] and exiting the battlefield, launches an attack at nearby enemies once every 2s (up to 4 times), dealing [red]4000%[/red] Physical DMG.",
                  "icon": "SS"
              },
              {
                  "name": "SSS Rank: I Am The Approaching Storm",
                  "description": "<strong>Lv. 1: [blue]Unlocked at SS3 Rank[/blue]</strong>\n Doppelganger’s joint attacks gain a [red]200%[/red] Extra DMG Bonus.\n After [red]Judgment Cut End[/red] is cast, [red]QTE: Judgment Cut Fall's[/red] Base DMG will increase by [red]1000%[/red] throughout the battle.\n\n<strong>Lv. 2: [blue]Unlocked at SSS Rank[/blue]</strong>\n Each JCE Point will increase [red]Judgment Cut End's[/red] Base DMG by [red]0.6%[/red]. [red]Judgment Cut End[/red] will deal an additional [red]120%[/red] Ultima Slash DMG per Truewill consumed.",
                  "icon": "SSS"
              },
              {
                  "name": "SSS+ Rank: Devil May Cry",
                  "description": "<strong>Lv. 1: [blue]Unlocked at SSS3 Rank[/blue]</strong>\n Signature Moves and additional damage dealt by [red]Judgment Cut End[/red] at the cost of Truewill gain a [red]30%[/red] Extra DMG Bonus.\n\n<strong>Lv. 2: [blue]Unlocked at SSS6 Rank[/blue]</strong>\n Basic Attacks, Judgment Cuts, and follow-up damage dealt by Judgment Cuts at the cost of Truewill gain a [red]50%[/red] Extra DMG Bonus.\n\n<strong>Lv. 3: [blue]Unlocked at SSS+ Rank[/blue]</strong>\n In SDT Form, Vergil gains a [red]20%[/red] Extra DMG Bonus.",
                  "icon": "SSS"
              }
