          "memory": "Build:Crepuscule",
          "bio": "This is a new specialized frame developed by the Science Council, based on further validation of the Phantom Tracer. It can disrupt Punishing information to some extent, effectively weakening its influence.",
          "effect": "<strong>Flow Divert</strong>\nBianca: Crepuscule enters the battlefield in [red]Twilight Form[/red]. She can only ping Red Orbs and the Blue Orb in [red]Twilight Form[/red], and she can only ping Yellow Orbs and the Blue Orb in [red]Radiance Form[/red].\n- Form shift triggered by tapping the Core Passive Bar: Shifting to [red]Twilight Form[/red] deals [red]120%[/red] Dark DMG. Shifting to [red]Radiance Form[/red] deals [red]120%[/red] Raydiance DMG.\n- Form shift triggered by pressing and holding the Core Passive Bar: Shifting to [red]Twilight Form[/red] deals [red]300%[/red] Dark DMG. Shifting to [red]Radiance Form[/red] deals [red]300%[/red] Raydiance DMG.\n- A form shift will clear [red]Commandment[/red], [red]Severed Sea[/red] stacks, the [red]Tidal Mark[/red], and [red]Prayer[/red] stacks.\n- Bianca: Crepuscule will pull in nearby enemies when consuming Radiant Crown stacks.\n\n<strong>Commandment</strong>\nCasting certain skills grants [red]Commandment[/red]. When [red]Commandment[/red] is full, Blue Orbs are activated.\n- Max [red]9 Commandment[/red].\n\n<strong>Abyssal Expansion: [blue]Twilight Form + Press and Hold Dodge[/blue]</strong>\nIn the Twilight Form, Bianca: Crepuscule cannot trigger the Matrix by successfully dodging attacks, but you can press and hold Dodge to make her perform space simulation and activate [red]Abyssal Domain[/red].\n- [red]Abyssal Domain[/red] has a 12-second cooldown.\n- Deals [red]600%[/red] Dark DMG in total when [red]Abyssal Domain[/red] is active. When [red]Abyssal Domain[/red] disappears, detonates the space and casts [red]Abyssal - Twilight Fall[/red], dealing [red]2400%[/red] Dark DMG and pulling in nearby enemies.\n-Red Orbs can be entered [red]3[/red] times when [red]Abyssal Domain[/red] is active. Each time when Red Orbs are entered, deals [red]200% / 400% / 600%[/red] Dark DMG and gains [red]1 / 2 / 3 Abyssal Value[/red], [red]1 / 2 / 3 Commandment[/red], and [red]1 / 2 / 5[/red] stacks of [red]Prayer[/red] based on the number of orbs pinged. \n- Max [red]9 Abyssal Value[/red]. The [red]Abyssal - Twilight Fall[/red] cast this time will consume all [red]Abyssal Value[/red]. [red]Each[/red] point consumed grants [red]1[/red] Signature Energy and [red]3[/red] stacks of [red]Prayer[/red] and increases the attack's Base DMG by [red]8%[/red], up to [red]72%[/red]. If having [red]9 Abyssal Value[/red] when casting the skill, gains extra [red]3[/red] Signature Energy and [red]8[/red] stacks of [red]Prayer[/red]. \n\n<strong>Repelling Guard: [blue]Radiance Form + Press and Hold Dodge[/blue]</strong>\nPressing and holding Dodge in Radiance Form will enter [red]Repelling Guard - Charge[/red], during which [red]Bianca: Crepuscule[/red] continuously gains [red]Commandment[/red] and Super Armor. When she is attacked during [red]Repelling Guard - Charge[/red], Dodge Gauge is consumed to dodge automatically, up to [red]1[/red] time, and Matrix cannot be triggered. Afterward, attacks will instead be blocked automatically, and Bianca gains [red]20%[/red] DMG Reduction when blocking. When the maximum duration is reached or Dodge is manually released, Bianca casts the corresponding skill and deals Raydiance DMG.\n- If Dodge is manually released, Bianca casts [red]Repelling Guard - Dodge[/red], dealing [red]360%[/red] Raydiance DMG and gaining [red]60 Raydiance Value[/red]. When the maximum duration is reached, Bianca instead casts [red]Repelling Guard - Spiral Slash[/red], dealing [red]420%[/red] Raydiance DMG and gaining [red]120 Raydiance Value[/red].\n- If the [red]Raydiance Gauge[/red] is full when casting [red]Repelling Guard - Dodge[/red] or [red]Repelling Guard - Spiral Slash[/red], Bianca enters the [red]Radiant Baptism Form[/red].\n- Bianca can dodge when casting [red]Repelling Guard - Dodge[/red] or [red]Repelling Guard - Spiral Slash[/red]. Upon a successful dodge, gains Super Armor for [red]2s[/red], [red]80%[/red] DMG Reduction, and [red]250[/red] Dodge.\n\n<strong>Effect: Raydiance</strong>\nAccumulates [red]Raydiance Gauge[/red]. When the gauge is full, Bianca can enter [red]Radiant Baptism Form[/red] through some skills and gain [red]10[/red] stacks of [red]Radiant Crown[/red]. Some skills consume [red]Radiant Crown[/red] stacks and grant enhancements while triggering [red]Radiant Embrace[/red] to deal Raydiance DMG.\n- [red]Raydiance Gauge[/red] is capped at [red]1000[/red] points.\n- [red]Radiant Embrace[/red] deals [red]330%[/red] Raydiance DMG.",
