                  "description": "<strong>Lv. 1: [blue]Unlocked at SS3 Rank[/blue]</strong>\n After casting [red]Abyssal Expansion[/red], [red]Twilight Form[/red] QTE Base DMG +[red]1000%[/red] throughout the battle. During [red]Devouring Sky[/red], can input an additional set of Signal Orbs. Based on the number of orbs pinged, Base DMG of [red]Devouring Sky - Collapsing Twilight[/red] cast this time increases by [red]60% / 120% / 180%[/red]. During [red]Shattering Sky[/red], can input an additional set of Signal Orbs, increasing the Base DMG of [red]Shattering Sky - Collapsing Radiance[/red] cast this time by [red]40% / 80% / 120%[/red]. Signal Orbs consumed this way will be refunded when the next [red]Shadow Strangle[/red] or [red]Ember Extinction[/red] is cast.\n\n<strong>Lv. 2: [blue]Unlocked at SSS Rank[/blue]</strong>\n During [red]Departed Mode[/red], when Bianca: Crepuscule is in [red]Twilight Form[/red], Extra DMG increases by [red]100%[/red]. Each [red]Prayer[/red] stack increases the damage of the [red]Shadow Strangle[/red] or [red]Ember Extinction[/red] cast this time by [red]0.009x[/red], up to [red]1.35x[/red].",
