          "memory": "Build:Secator",
          "bio": "A new frame designed by Babylonia. Compared to Kurono's older model, its M.I.N.D. is less stable, with output levels prone to wide fluctuations.",
          "effect": "<strong>Silent Rampancy</strong> \n While in [red]Silent Consent[/red], only Blue and Yellow Orbs can be used. Under [red]Rampant Disaster[/red], only Red Orbs can be used.\n\n<strong>Final Rite</strong> \n When casting Yellow or Blue Orb skills, [red]Converging Edge[/red] grants [red]Cutting Edge[/red]. Casting [red]Purgatory Shear[/red] or [red]Focused Rending[/red] will consume all [red]Cutting Edge[/red] and increase the Base DMG of [red]Purgatory Shear[/red] and [red]Focused Rending[/red] based on the [red]Cutting Edge[/red] consumed. \n - Each Yellow or Blue Orb grants [red]5 Cutting Edge[/red], and each point of [red]Cutting Edge[/red] increases the Base DMG of [red]Purgatory Shear[/red] and [red]Focused Rending[/red] by [red]1%[/red].\n\n<strong>Converging Edge: [blue]Press and hold Dodge to enter Disentangle[/blue]</strong> \n Press and hold Dodge to enter [red]Disentangle[/red] and gain [red]Cutting Edge[/red] over time. When the status is active, gains Super Armor, becomes unable to restore Dodge Gauge, and can trigger Block once. Gains brief Invincibility after successful Block. During [red]Disentangle[/red], automatically performs 3-Pings and provides an Extra DMG Bonus to [red]Purgatory Shear[/red]. \n - Each 3-Ping provides [red]45%[/red] Extra DMG Bonus to [red]Purgatory Shear[/red]. Max [red]2[/red] 3-Pings can be performed.\n\n<strong>Purgatory Shear: [blue]Press and hold Dodge to enter Disentangle, then release Dodge[/blue]</strong> \n Press and hold Dodge to enter [red]Disentangle[/red]. Then, release to dodge, launch a powerful slash, and consume all [red]Cutting Edge[/red], dealing Physical DMG and gaining Signature Energy and Sharp Reserve based on the [red]Cutting Edge[/red] consumed. \n - Deals [red]125%[/red] Physical DMG and gains [red]75 Sharp Reserve[/red] for [red]0-15 Cutting Edge[/red] consumed. \n - Deals [red]250%[/red] Physical DMG and gains [red]150 Sharp Reserve[/red] for [red]16-30 Cutting Edge[/red] consumed. \n - Deals [red]500%[/red] Physical DMG and gains [red]300 Sharp Reserve[/red] for [red]31-45 Cutting Edge[/red] consumed. \n - [red]Each point[/red] of [red]Cutting Edge[/red] consumed grants [red]1[/red] Signature Energy and increases the Base DMG of [red]Purgatory Shear[/red] by [red]1%[/red].\n\n<strong>Effect: Ultima Slash</strong>\nCertain skills build up [red]Sharp Reserve[/red]. [red]Sharp Reserve[/red] can be passed on to the next character affected by Ultima Slash effect, up to a maximum of [red]999[/red] points.\n- When [red]Sharp Reserve[/red] reaches [red]100[/red] points, the next skill with a [red]Ultima Slash[/red] effect that hits an enemy will consume [red]100 points of Sharp Reserve[/red] to trigger a [red]Ultima Slash[/red], dealing [red]400%[/red] Ultima Slash DMG.\n- Gains [red]1[/red] point of [red]Truewill[/red] each time it triggers, up to a maximum of [red]90[/red] points.",
