          "bio": "A former member of the Church of Machina, who left the organization for various reasons and now operates independently. Prefers expressing herself through force rather than words.",
          "effect": "<strong>Raid Support</strong>\nDuring [red]Adjudication[/red], only Blue Orbs and Yellow Orb can be used. Basic attacks only generate Blue Orbs.\n- During [red]Execution[/red], only Red Orbs and Yellow Orb can be used. Basic attacks only generate Red Orbs.\n- When entering [red]Execution[/red], unused Blue Orbs from [red]Adjudication[/red] are retained and [red]Chaos Value[/red] is cleared.\n- When exiting [red]Execution[/red], unused Red Orbs are cleared and [red]Sin Mark[/red] is removed.\n- When [red]exiting the battlefield[/red], [red]Rekindle[/red] stacks and [red]Chaos Value[/red] are retained, [red]Searing Sight[/red] is removed, and [red]Purge Value[/red] and White Orbs in the secondary orb slot are cleared.\n- [red]Chaos Value[/red] cap is [red]100[/red]. Can cast [red]Severing Domain[/red] when Chaos Value reaches [red]100[/red].\n- [red]Purge Value[/red] cap is [red]100[/red]. Can cast [red]Torrential Blast[/red] when [red]Purge Value is at least 1[/red].\n\n<strong>Blazing Star: [blue]Execution Airborne + Tap or Press and Hold Dodge When Not Moving Joystick / Press and Hold Dodge When Moving Joystick[/blue]</strong>\nVeronica: Aegis wields her Lance to perform consecutive thrusts in the air, dealing DMG and recovering Red Orbs.\n- Can only be cast while airborne during [red]Execution[/red], dealing [red]160%[/red] Physical DMG.\n- When having [red]Searing Sight[/red], deals [red]160%[/red] Ignition DMG instead.\n- Each cast recovers 1 Red Orb.\n- When casting [red]Blazing Star[/red], a dodge check will be performed. Successfully dodging will trigger Matrix if it is not on cooldown.\n\n<strong>Molten Blaze</strong>\nAllies healed by Veronica: Aegis gain the [red]Ultralimit Torque[/red] effect that increases Physical DMG by [red]20%[/red] for [red]8[/red]s. Duration resets every time it is triggered.\n- When the team has [red]Ignition[/red] effect, allies healed by Veronica: Aegis instead gain the [red]Fire Tempered[/red] effect that increases Fire DMG by [red]20%[/red] for [red]8[/red]s. Duration resets every time it is triggered.\n\n<strong>Relit</strong>\nEach stack of [red]Ember Mark[/red] increases Ignition Effect Base DMG by [red]5%[/red]. Stacks up to [red]15[/red] times.\n\n<strong>Effect: Ignition</strong>\nCombustible: Every [red]250[/red] Combustible Charges will add [red]1[/red] Combustible stack, up to 20 stacks.\n- Ignition: Ignited units take Ignition DMG equal to [red]Ignition stacks x30%[/red]  every second (Tank Skills will not be triggered) for 10s.\n- The subsequent unit will inherit the Combustible/Ignition status of the last unit on the battlefield upon its death.",
