                  "description": "<strong>Blazing Desolation: [blue]During Adjudication + 60 Signature Energy + Tap/Press and Hold Signature[/blue]</strong>\nVeronica: Aegis leaps into the air and arms herself. When casting, triggers Time Lag Calculation and enters [red]Execution[/red], gaining [red]9[/red] Red Orbs.\n- Deals a total of [red]1800%[/red] Physical DMG in 3 hits.\n- When casting by holding the button, deals a total of [red]1800%[/red] Ignition DMG instead, and gains [red]Searing Sight[/red].\n\n<strong>Ruinous Ember: [blue]During Execution + 90 Signature Energy + Tap Signature[/blue]</strong>\nVeronica: Aegis transforms into dragon form and crashes into the ground, dealing DMG. Triggers Time Lag Calculation when casting, then exits [red]Execution[/red] and enters [red]Adjudication[/red]. Leaves behind [red]Vital Void[/red] after casting, continuously restoring HP for allied units within.\n- Deals a total of [red]400%[/red] Physical DMG in 5 hits.\n- When having [red]Searing Sight[/red], deals [red]5000%[/red] Ignition DMG instead and clears [red]Searing Sight[/red]. Converts [red]Rekindle[/red] into corresponding stacks of [red]Ember Mark[/red] for [red]24[/red]s. Duration resets every time it is triggered. Converts [red]Combustible[/red] into equal stacks of [red]Ignition[/red]. If already in [red]Ignition[/red], refreshes the current [red]Ignition[/red] duration. The first cast upon entering the field grants [red]1 Ignition Stack[/red] per second to targets in [red]Ignition[/red], up to [red]8[/red] times.\n- If having [red]Field Ultralimit[/red] when casting, refreshes its duration.\n- After casting, leaves behind [red]Vital Void[/red] that lasts for [red]12[/red]s, restoring HP equal to [red]20%[/red] of Veronica: Aegis's ATK per second for allied units within.",
