                  "description": "<strong>QTE – [blue]Tap QTE[/blue]</strong>\nDeals damage and heals.\n- Deals a total of [red]600%[/red] Physical DMG.\n- If having [red]Ember Mark[/red], deals [red]600%[/red] Ignition DMG instead.\n- Restores HP equal to [red]100%[/red] of ATK.",
