          "memory": "Build:Limpidity",
          "bio": "Developed by the Science Council, this new frame integrates data from the Golden Age's Phylotree of Ousia project into the M.I.N.D. Its success marks the dawn of a new era.",
          "effect": "<strong>First Light</strong> \n Gains a set of 3-Ping Orbs every time upon entering battle.\n\n<strong>Heavenly Flash: [blue]4 Flying Blades + Pres and Hold Dodge[/blue]</strong> \n Summons a massive lightning strike to attack. When casting, can trigger lightning chain and gather enemies, dealing DMG; triggers Matrix if it is not on cooldown. Consumes all [red]Flying Blades[/red] and gains [red]45[/red] Signature Energy. Also gains Super Armor and [red]70%[/red] DMG Reduction when casting. \n - Deals [red]2700%[/red] Lightning DMG\n\n<strong>Mirror Flight: [blue]During Dream Dive + Tap Mirror Blade Orb[/blue]</strong> \n During Dream Dive, the rightmost slot of the Signal Orb bar is fixed as [red]Mirror Blade Orb[/red]. When repeatedly tapping the [red]Mirror Blade Orb[/red], consumes [red]White Orbs[/red] to deal DMG and gain [red]Flow Points[/red], [red]Delicate Heart[/red], and Signature Energy. Also gains Super Armor and [red]50%[/red] DMG Reduction when casting. \n Deals a total of [red]8800%[/red] Lightning DMG. \n Each [red]White Orb[/red] consumed grants [red]25 Flow Points[/red] and [red]25 Sonance[/red]. \n Based on the number of Signature Points cast, gains [red]6 / 6/ 9 / 9 Signature Energy[/red] and [red]1 / 1 / 2 / 2[/red] stacks of [red]Delicate Heart[/red]. \n - When in [red]Darkcross Form[/red], deals a total of [red]11200%[/red] Darkflow DMG instead.\n\n<strong>Dawn Dream: [blue]During Dream Dive + Flow Points ≥50 + Press and Hold Basic Attack or Mirror Blade Orb[/blue]</strong> \n Leaps into the air to pull in enemies and crush them, consuming [red]Flow Points[/red] to deal DMG and gain [red]Delicate Heart[/red] and Signature Energy. Invincible when casting. \n - Consumes [red]50 Flow Points[/red] to cast [red]Startled Dream[/red], dealing [red]2200%[/red] Lightning DMG and gaining [red]2[/red] stacks of [red]Delicate Heart[/red] and [red]8[/red] Signature Energy. When in [red]Darkcross Form[/red], deals [red]2800%[/red] Darkflow DMG instead. \n - During [red]Startled Dream[/red], press and hold [red]Basic Attack[/red] to consume another [red]50 Flow Points[/red] and cast [red]Light Seeker[/red], dealing [red]2600%[/red] Lightning DMG and gaining [red]4[/red] stacks of [red]Delicate Heart[/red], [red]40[/red] Signature Energy, and [red]1[/red] Signal Orb. When in [red]Darkcross Form[/red], deals [red]3400%[/red] Darkflow DMG instead. \n - [red]Flow Points[/red] is capped at [red]100[/red].\n\n<strong>Stacked Light: [blue]During Dream Dive + Press and Hold Dodge[/blue]</strong> \n Continuously launches shattered mirror attacks, dealing Lightning DMG. Pressing and holding Dodge automatically pings Signal Orbs during this time, up to [red]4[/red] times, then detonates enemies and casts [red]Thousand Rays[/red], dealing Lightning DMG, while gaining enhancement effects based on the number of orbs pinged. Gains Super Armor and [red]70%[/red] DMG Reduction when casting. Can only cast [red]Stacked Light[/red] once during Dream Dive. \n Sustained attacks deal [red]400%[/red] Lightning DMG. [red]Thousand Rays[/red] deals [red]200%[/red] Lightning DMG. \n - When in [red]Darkcross Form[/red], sustained attacks deal [red]400%[/red] Darkflow DMG and [red]Thousand Rays[/red] deals [red]2900%[/red] Darkflow DMG. \n - Each Signal Orb consumed increases this [red]Thousand Rays[/red]'s Base DMG by [red]20%[/red]. When consuming 3-Ping Orbs, gains [red]2[/red] additional Signature Energy and [red]1[/red] stack of [red]Delicate Heart[/red]. \n - [red]White Orbs[/red] will be prioritized during the skill. Can consume [red]2 White Orbs[/red] at once, which are treated as one 3-Ping Orb set. When fewer than [red]2 White Orbs[/red] are available, can consume [red]1 White Orb[/red], which is treated as [red]1[/red] Signal Orb. \n - If [red]12[/red] Signal Orbs are pinged during the skill, gains [red]1[/red] Signal Orb after casting.\n\n<strong>Effect: Darkflow</strong> \n Every [red]200[/red] Darkflow Reserve grants 1 Darkflow stack, up to a maximum of 15. Characters with the Darkflow Effect will gain a Darkflow Aura based on the current Darkflow stacks, dealing a small amount of Darkflow DMG over time to enemies and reducing their HP recovery. When the Darkflow stacks reach the threshold, the Aura upgrades, increasing its area of effect and dealing massive Darkflow DMG to enemies within the area. \n - [red]1 / 3 / 6 / 10 / 15[/red] stacks: Deals [red]100% / 200% / 400% / 800% / 1600%[/red] Darkflow DMG, then deals [red]20% / 40% / 60% / 80% / 100%[/red] Darkflow DMG per second, reducing enemy HP recovery by [red]10% / 20% / 30% / 50% / 100%[/red].",
