                  "name": "Red Orb: Sinful Peak — Red Orb",
                  "description": "<strong>Crushing Supremacy: [blue]Forest Guard Mimic + Crusher Module + Tap Red Orb[/blue]</strong>\nFires a laser, pinging White Signal Orbs to deal DMG and enter Crushing Supremacy combo.\n- Pings [red]0/1[/red] White Signal Orb to deal [red]200% / 1000%[/red] Dark DMG and gain [red]0/20 Light Links[/red] and [red]0/4 Signature Energy[/red].\n- When the team carries [red]Ultima Slash[/red] effect, pings [red]0 / 1[/red] White Signal Orb to deal [red]100% / 600%[/red] Ultima Slash DMG instead and gain [red]0 / 20 Light Links[/red] and [red]0 / 4 Signature Energy[/red].\n\n'''Halberd's Burden: [blue]Forest Guard Mimic + Crushing Supremacy Combo + Tap Red Orb[/blue]<strong>\nTurns around and fires two lasers, pinging White Signal Orbs to deal DMG.\n- Pings [red]0 / 1 / 2[/red] White Signal Orbs to deal [red]400% / 800% / 2000%[/red] Dark DMG and gain [red]0 / 20/ 40 Light Links[/red] and [red]0 /4 / 8 Signature Energy[/red].\n- When the team carries [red]Ultima Slash[/red] effect, pings [red]0 / 1 / 2[/red] White Signal Orbs to deal [red]200% / 400% / 1200%[/red] Ultima Slash DMG instead and gains [red]0 / 20 / 40 Light Links[/red] and [red]0 / 4 / 8 Signature Energy[/red].\n- Pinging [red]2[/red] White Signal Orbs counts as a 3-Ping.\n\n</strong>Halberd of Conviction: [blue]Nessos Mimic + Crusher Module + Continuously Tap Red Orb[/blue]'''\nSlashes forward with the halberd and unleashes swordwaves, dealing DMG.\n- Arete performs a 2-hit attack under [red]Crusher Module[/red], dealing [red]180% / 180%[/red] Dark DMG. Can consume [red]6 / 6 Overridden Blessing[/red] to deal [red] 1800% / 1800%[/red] Dark DMG instead and gain [red]2 / 2 Signature Energy[/red].\n- When the team carries [red]Ultima Slash[/red] effect, deals [red]100% / 100%[/red] Ultima Slash DMG instead. Can consume [red]6 / 6 Overridden Blessing[/red] to deal [red] 1000% / 1000%[/red] Ultima Slash DMG instead and gain [red]2 / 2 Signature Energy[/red].",
