                  "description": "<strong>Withering Tempo: [blue]Forest Guard Mimic + Piercer Module + Tap Blue Orb[/blue]</strong>\nDashes forward and thrusts the weapon, pinging White Signal Orbs to deal DMG and enter [red]Withering Tempo[/red] combo.\n- Pings [red]0 / 1[/red] White Signal Orb to deal [red]200% / 1000%[/red] Dark DMG and gain [red]0 / 20 Light Links[/red] and [red]0 / 4 Signature Energy[/red].\n - When the team carries [red]Ultima Slash[/red] effect, pings [red]0 / 1[/red] White Signal Orb to deal [red]100% / 600%[/red] Ultima Slash DMG instead and gain [red]0 / 20 Light Links[/red] and [red]0 / 4 Signature Energy[/red].\n\n<strong>Parallel Suppression: [blue]Forest Guard Mimic + Withering Tempo Combo + Tap Blue Orb[/blue]</strong>\nTurns around and slashes to release multiple swordwaves, pinging White Signal Orbs to deal DMG.\n- Pings [red]0 / 1 / 2[/red] White Signal Orbs to deal [red]400% / 800% / 2000%[/red] Dark DMG and gain [red]0 / 20 / 40 Light Links[/red] and [red]0 / 4 / 8 Signature Energy[/red].\n- When the team carries [red]Ultima Slash[/red] effect, pings [red]0 / 1 / 2[/red] White Signal Orbs to deal [red]200% / 400% / 1200%[/red] Ultima Slash DMG instead and gains [red]0 / 20 / 40 Light Links[/red] and [red]0 / 4 / 8 Signature Energy[/red].\n- Pinging 2 White Signal Orbs counts as a 3-Ping.\n\n<strong>Collective Pivot: [blue]Nessos Mimic + Piercer Module + Continuously Tap Blue Orb[/blue]</strong>\nDashes forward with the halberd and performs a downward slash, dealing DMG.\n - Arete performs a 2-hit attack under [red]Piercer Module[/red], dealing [red]240% / 480%[/red] Dark DMG. Can consume [red]10 / 20  Overridden Blessing[/red] to deal [red]2400% /4800%[/red] Dark DMG instead and gain [red]4 / 6 Signature Energy[/red].\n- When the team carries [red]Ultima Slash[/red] effect, deals [red]160% / 320%[/red] Ultima Slash DMG instead. Can consume [red]10 / 20 Overridden Blessing[/red] to deal [red]1600% / 3200%[/red] Ultima Slash DMG instead and gain [red]4 / 6 Signature Energy[/red].",
